PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?q ?langcode ?langLabel (COUNT(?label) AS ?count) WHERE {
VALUES ?q {wd:[entity:Ferdowsikara]}
?q (rdfs:label|skos:altLabel) ?label
BIND(LANG(?label) AS ?langcode)
?lang wdt:[property:ISO 639-1 code] ?langcode
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} GROUP BY ?q ?langcode ?langLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?count)

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?workLabel ?pubdate ?pubdatePrecision ?image ?typelabel ?english
(URI(CONCAT("https://tools.wmflabs.org/reasonator/?q=", SUBSTR(STR(?work),32) )) as ?reasonator) #build a reasonator link
(IF(BOUND(?english), ?english, ?reasonator) as ?link) # link to English Wikipedia article, if available
WHERE {
?work wdt:[property:author] wd:[entity:Voltaire]; # author: Voltaire
wdt:[property:instance of] ?type; # What is the work? poem, play, historical work etc.?
p:[property:publication date]/psv:[property:publication date] ?pubdateStatementNode
MINUS {?work wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:version, edition or translation]} # exclude editions
MINUS {?work wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:anthology]} # exclude anthologies
?pubdateStatementNode wikibase:timeValue ?pubdate ;
wikibase:timePrecision ?pubdatePrecision # get precision of the publication date
OPTIONAL {?work wdt:[property:image] ?image}
OPTIONAL{ ?english schema:about ?work ; schema:isPartOf <https://en.wikipedia.org/> }
SERVICE wikibase:label {bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "fr,en,de"} # Prefer labels in French but fall back to English and German
?type rdfs:label ?typelabel FILTER(lang(?typelabel) ="en") # English labels for the types
}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?work ?workLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?sitelink) as ?linkcount) WHERE {
?work wdt:[property:author] wd:[entity:Voltaire]. # works by Voltaire
MINUS {?work wdt:[property:instance of] wd:Q39811647} # translations
MINUS {?work wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:version, edition or translation]} # editions
MINUS {?work wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:anthology]} # anthologies
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en,fr,de". }
OPTIONAL{?sitelink schema:about ?work . # get Wikimedia pages about the work
FILTER(CONTAINS(str(?sitelink), ".wikipedia.org/")) } # only Wikipedia links
} GROUP BY ?work ?workLabel ORDER BY DESC(?linkcount)

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?coord ?birthyear ?birthplace ?name ?person WHERE {
{?person wdt:[property:occupation] wd:[entity:economist] } UNION {?person wdt:[property:field of work] wd:[entity:economics]} MINUS {?person wdt:[property:occupation] wd:[entity:economist]; wdt:[property:field of work] wd:[entity:economics]}
?person wdt:[property:place of birth] ?place .
?place wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord .
OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dob }.
MINUS { ?person wdt:[property:date of death] ?dod }.
BIND(YEAR(?dob) as ?birthyear).
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". ?person rdfs:label ?name. ?place rdfs:label ?birthplace}
}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>

PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personLabel ?award ?awardLabel ?year WHERE {
?person p:[property:award received] ?statement.
?statement ps:[property:award received] ?award.
?award wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:economics award]
OPTIONAL { ?statement pq:[property:point in time] ?date. BIND(YEAR(?date) AS ?year) }
MINUS{ ?person wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]? wd:[entity:fictional human] } # exclude fictional people
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en" }
} ORDER BY ASC(?awardLabel) ASC(?year)

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personLabel (COUNT(?award) AS ?awards) (GROUP_CONCAT(?awardLabel; separator=", ") as ?list) WHERE {
?person wdt:[property:award received] ?award.
?award wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:economics award]
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en" . ?award rdfs:label ?awardLabel . ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel }
} GROUP BY ?person ?personLabel
HAVING ( ?awards > 1 )
ORDER BY DESC(?awards)

SELECT ?college ?collegeLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?alum) AS ?count)
WHERE {
{?college wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:college of the University of Oxford]} UNION {?college wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:Permanent Private Hall]}. # college or private hall

?person rdfs:label ?name filter (lang(?name) = "en")

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?thing ?thingLabel ?city ?cityLabel ?distnum WHERE {
?thing wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity] ?city; wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?thingloc.
?city wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:city]; wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?cityloc.

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?label ?subj (SAMPLE(?whereLabel) AS ?where) (SAMPLE(?countryLabel) as ?country) (SAMPLE(?orderLabel) AS ?order) WHERE
{ ?subj wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]? ?type ;
rdfs:label ?label filter (lang(?label) = "en")
?type wdt:[property:subclass of]? wd:[entity:monastery]. # instance of monastery or subtype
OPTIONAL { ?subj wdt:[property:country]/rdfs:label ?countryLabel filter (lang(?countryLabel) = "en") }
OPTIONAL { ?subj wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]/rdfs:label ?whereLabel filter (lang(?whereLabel) = "en") }
OPTIONAL { ?subj wdt:[property:religious order]/rdfs:label ?orderLabel filter (lang(?orderLabel) = "en") }
MINUS {?subj wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:France] } # not France
MINUS {?subj wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:Republic of Ireland] } # not Ireland
?subj p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location] ?loc. # coordinate-location statement
?loc wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat .
?loc wikibase:geoLongitude ?long .
FILTER (?lat > 50) FILTER (?lat < 63)
FILTER (?long > -10.5) FILTER (?long < 2.02)
} GROUP BY ?label ?subj
ORDER BY ?label

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT ?work ?workLabel ?artistLabel ?date ?datePrecision ?image WHERE {
?work wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:painting] # paintings
; wdt:[property:creator] ?artist .
?artist wdt:[property:country of citizenship] wd:[entity:Russian Empire]. # artist's nationality: Russian Empire
?work p:[property:inception]/psv:[property:inception] ?node .
?node wikibase:timeValue ?date ; # date of painting

BIND(YEAR(?date) as ?year) FILTER(?year > 1905) FILTER(?year < 1930) #specify date range
FILTER (?datePrecision > 8) # known year
.?work wdt:[property:image] ?image # only show art that Commons has an image for
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en,ru,et,de,fr". }
}

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdno: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/novalue/>

SELECT ?game ?date ?statementNodeType ?check0 ?check1 ?check2 ?check3
WHERE
{
VALUES ?game {
wd:[entity:Bob's Game] # no value
wd:[entity:64 Hanafuda: Tenshi no Yakusoku] # one value
wd:[entity:Battlefleet Gothic: Armada] # unknown value
wd:[entity:Civilization V] # multiple values
wd:Q23647080 # no property
}
OPTIONAL
{
?game p:[property:publication date] ?statementNode
OPTIONAL { ?statementNode ps:[property:publication date] ?date }
OPTIONAL { ?statementNode rdf:type ?statementNodeType FILTER (?statementNodeType IN (wdno:[property:publication date])) }
}
BIND(IF(BOUND(?statementNode),true,false) as ?check0) # property is here?
BIND(COALESCE(DATATYPE(?date) = xsd:dateTime , false) as ?check1) # real date?
BIND(COALESCE((wdno:[property:publication date] = ?statementNodeType), false) as ?check2) # no value?
BIND(COALESCE(isBlank(?date) , false) as ?check3) # unknown?
}

WHERE
{
#for selected items
VALUES ?item {
wd:[entity:Adolf Lorenz]
wd:[entity:anonymous]
}
?item ?prefix ?valueorstatementnode.
BIND(xsd:integer(IF(fn:starts-with(STR(?prefix), "http://www.wikidata.org/prop/P"), fn:replace(STR(?prefix), "http://www.wikidata.org/prop/P", ""), "???")) as ?pid)
BIND(IRI(CONCAT("http://www.wikidata.org/prop/novalue/P", STR(?pid))) as ?possibleWDNO)
OPTIONAL
{
?valueorstatementnode rdf:type ?typeOfStatementNode. # information about "no value" stored as type
}
BIND(IF(isBlank(?valueorstatementnode), "unknown value", IF(?typeOfStatementNode = ?possibleWDNO, "no value", ?value)) as ?customText)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en" }
}
ORDER BY DESC(?customText)

}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?subject ?subjectLabel ?subjectDescription (year(?date) as ?year) WHERE {
?subject p:[property:date of birth]/psv:[property:date of birth] ?date_node . # node for date of birth
?date_node wikibase:timePrecision "11"^^xsd:integer . # date precision = day
?date_node wikibase:timeValue ?date .
FILTER (day(?date) = day(now())) . # day of birth date is day of current date
FILTER (month(?date) = month(now())) . # month of birth date is month of current date
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?date
LIMIT 100

PREFIX wdno: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/novalue/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?human ?humanLabel
WHERE
{
?human wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] . #find humans
?human p:[property:child] ?childStatement . #with at least one [property:child] (child) statement
?childStatement rdf:type wdno:[property:child] . #where the [property:child] (child) statement is defined to be "no value"
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en" . }
}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription ?sitelinks
WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human]; # Any instance of a human
wdt:[property:place of birth]/wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]* wd:[entity:New York City]; # Who was born in any value (eg. a hospital)
wikibase:sitelinks ?sitelinks.

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?articlename ?itemLabel ?itemDescription ?sl
WHERE {
VALUES ?dod {"+2001-08-25"^^xsd:dateTime}
?dod ^wdt:[property:date of death] ?item .
?item wikibase:sitelinks ?sl .
?item ^schema:about ?article .
?article schema:isPartOf <https://en.wikipedia.org/>;
schema:name ?articlename .
SERVICE wikibase:label
{
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en" .
?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel .
?item schema:description ?itemDescription .
}
BIND(REPLACE(?itemLabel, "^.*(?<! [Vv][ao]n| [Dd][aeiu]| [Dd][e][lns]| [Ll][ae]) (?!([SJ]r\\.?|[XVI]+)$)", "") AS ?sortname)
} ORDER BY ASC(UCASE(?sortname)) ASC(UCASE(?itemLabel))

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX ontolex: <http://www.w3.org/ns/lemon/ontolex#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?lexemeId ?lemma ?q_concept ?q_conceptDescription ?picture
WHERE {
?lexemeId dct:language wd:[entity:German]; # change language here
wikibase:lemma ?lemma;
ontolex:sense ?sense.
?sense wdt:[property:item for this sense] ?q_concept.
?q_concept wdt:[property:image] ?picture.
############
# Exclusions
############
# Exclude out of scope concepts
MINUS {?q_concept wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:sovereign state].}. # countries
# Exclude non suitable concepts
VALUES ?minus {
wd:[entity:rape] # rape
wd:[entity:war] # war
wd:[entity:violence] # violence
wd:[entity:revolver] # revolver
wd:[entity:cigar] #cigar
#... add yours here
}.
MINUS {?sense wdt:[property:item for this sense] ?minus.}.
# Exclude senses not suitable for young children:
VALUES ?filter {
wd:[entity:slang]
wd:[entity:pejorative]
wd:[entity:vulgarism]
wd:[entity:profanity]}.
FILTER NOT EXISTS {?sense wdt:[property:language style] ?filter.}.
# if you wish to only browse certain items you can insert a FILTER
# regular expression here, like in the example above.
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "de,en". }
}
ORDER BY lcase(?lemma) # order a-z

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?languageLabel (COUNT(?example) AS ?count ) WHERE {
?l a ontolex:LexicalEntry; dct:language ?language.
?l p:[property:usage example] ?statement.
?statement ps:[property:usage example] ?example;
pq:[property:subject sense] [];
pq:[property:subject form] [].
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

SELECT ?lang (COUNT(DISTINCT ?article) AS ?count) WHERE {
hint:Query hint:optimizer "None".

} GROUP BY ?lang

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?place ?location ?elev ?image
WHERE
{
  ?place p:[property:elevation above sea level]/psv:[property:elevation above sea level] ?placeElev.
  ?placeElev wikibase:quantityAmount ?elev.
  ?placeElev wikibase:quantityUnit ?unit.
  bind(0.01 as ?km).
  filter( (?elev < ?km*1000 && ?unit = wd:[entity:metre])
       || (?elev < ?km*3281 && ?unit = wd:[entity:foot])
       || (?elev < ?km      && ?unit = wd:[entity:kilometre]) ).
  ?place wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?location.
  OPTIONAL { ?place wdt:[property:image] ?image }
  SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en" }
}

SELECT ?muni ?muniLabel ?location where {
?muni p:[property:instance of] ?instanceOf; # Get statement because we need this later

}

WHERE {
VALUES ?biomarker {wd:[entity:phosphoribosyl pyrophosphate] wd:[entity:5-formamido-1-(5-phospho-D-ribosyl)imidazole-4-carboxamide(2-)] wd:[entity:guanosine]} #you can add more biomarkers here if needed, separated by a space.
?biomarker wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:chemical compound]. #Stating that all biomarkers have to be "instance of" "chemical compound" (you could ommit this, but query will probably take longer).
?biomarker wdt:[property:PDB structure ID] ?pdbID . #Checking if a biomarker has a Protein Databank ID (PDB) -> meaning the metabolite can interact with a protein.
?protein wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:protein] . #Stating that all proteins are "instance of" "protein"
?protein wdt:[property:PDB structure ID] ?pdbID . #Checking which proteins have a PDB ID, which we queried previously in relationship to the biomarkers.
?protein wdt:[property:encoded by] ?gene . #Connecting the protein to a gene ("encoded by" relationship) -> to get an identifier we can use later in federated WikiPathways query.
?gene wdt:[property:found in taxon] wd:[entity:Homo sapiens] . #Now removing all genes that are not found in species "Homo sapiens". -> This info is not always available for proteins in WikiData.
?gene wdt:[property:exact match] ?geneID . #Getting the "exact match" identifier for the gene, related to the protein, related to the biomarker.
##The IRI from Wikidata starts with http:// , where the one from WikiPathways starts with https:// , so we need to rewrite the IRI
BIND( # Bind the created IRI into a new variable (called ?newIRI)
IRI( # Convert the string back to an IRI
CONCAT( # Concatenate item 1 and 2 together as one string
"https", # First item to concat (more items can be added with a comma
#Second item to concat:
SUBSTR( # Obtain a substring
STR(?geneID), # Convert the geneID IRI from Wikidata to a string,
5) # removing the first 5 characters (<http)
)) AS ?newIRI # Name for the new variable
)
SERVICE <http://sparql.wikipathways.org/sparql> { #Connecting to the WikiPathways SPARQL endpoint.
?WP_pathway a wp:Pathway . #Stating a ?WP_pathway is indeed a pathway in the WikiPathways RDF .
?WP_pathway wp:organismName "Homo sapiens" . #Removing all PWs not for species Homo sapiens.
?WP_pathway dc:identifier ?PathwayID . #Query the identifier of the pathway in WPs.
?WP_pathway dc:title ?PathwayName . #Obtaining the name of the pathway.
?WP_gene a wp:Protein . #Stating that a ?WP_gene is a Protein DataNode (you could ommit this, to also get all DataNodes modeled as GeneProducts out, but query will take longer).
?WP_gene wp:bdbEntrezGene ?newIRI . #Connecting the previously queried "exact match" from WikiData to the NCBI/Entrez Gene ID in WPs.
?WP_gene dcterms:isPartOf ?WP_pathway . #Connecting the WP_gene to the WP_pathway.
}
OPTIONAL {?biomarker rdfs:label ?biomarkerLabel. #Create a label (aka name) for the biomarkers in WikiData, without using the service query.
FILTER(LANG(?biomarkerLabel) = "en").
}
OPTIONAL {?protein rdfs:label ?proteinLabel. #Create a label(aka name) for the proteins in WikiData, without using the service query.
FILTER(LANG(?proteinLabel) = "en").
}
}
ORDER BY DESC (?biomarkerLabel) #Order results for biomarkers

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?h ?hLabel ?inception ?dissolved ?coor
WHERE
{
  VALUES ?countryclass { wd:[entity:historical country] wd:[entity:country] wd:[entity:sovereign state] }
  ?h p:[property:instance of]/ps:[property:instance of] ?countryclass .
  ?h wdt:[property:inception] ?inception .

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?person ?personLabel ?dob ?dod (xsd:integer(?age_) as ?age)
where {
# We do a subquery here, because otherwise we'll get a timeout because of the labels
{
SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?dob ?dod ?age_
where {
?person wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human]; # Get all humans
wdt:[property:occupation]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:musician]; # That have a musician or a subclass thereof as their occupation
p:[property:date of birth] ?dob_st; # death of birth
p:[property:date of death] ?dod_st. # death of death
?dob_st psv:[property:date of birth] [ wikibase:timeValue ?dob; wikibase:timePrecision ?dob_prec ];
a wikibase:BestRank.
?dod_st psv:[property:date of death] [ wikibase:timeValue ?dod; wikibase:timePrecision ?dod_prec ];
a wikibase:BestRank.
# Only accept date precisions of a day or better, so it doesn't cause problems when we calculate age
FILTER(?dob_prec >= 11 && ?dod_prec >= 11)
# Time differences in Blazegraph are counted as days and is xsd:double
# We then calculate the age by dividing this by the orbital period of Earth
# This is a shortcut, but it is accurate enough for our purposes
bind((?dod - ?dob) / 365.2564 as ?age_)
# And filter by age
filter(?age_ >= 27.0 && ?age_ < 28.0)
}
#LIMIT 1000
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY desc(?dod) # Order by most recent

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?wikiciteLabel ?doi WHERE {
?wikicite p:[property:DOI]/ps:[property:DOI] ?doi .
?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom ?ref .
?ref pr:[property:DOI] ?doi .
FILTER (CONTAINS(lcase(?doi), "figshare"))
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

query:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?writer ?label
WHERE
{
# French writer born in the second half of the 18th century
?writer wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human];
wdt:[property:country of citizenship] wd:[entity:France];
wdt:[property:occupation] wd:[entity:writer];
wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dob.
FILTER("1751-01-01"^^xsd:dateTime <= ?dob && ?dob < "1801-01-01"^^xsd:dateTime).
# get the English label
?writer rdfs:label ?writerLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?writerLabel) = "en").
# get the pseudonym, if it exists
OPTIONAL { ?writer wdt:[property:pseudonym] ?pseudonym. }
# bind the pseudonym, or if it doesn't exist the English label, as ?label
BIND(IF(BOUND(?pseudonym),?pseudonym,?writerLabel) AS ?label).
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ?director ?director_label (count(distinct ?film) as ?films) (count(distinct ?sitelink) as ?sitelinks) ((?films * ?sitelinks) as ?rank)
WHERE
{
?director wdt:[property:occupation] wd:[entity:film director] . # has "film director" as occupation
?film wdt:[property:director] ?director . # get all films directed by the director
?sitelink schema:about ?director . # get all the sitelinks about the director
OPTIONAL {?director rdfs:label ?director_label # get the label of the director (if it exists)
FILTER (lang(?director_label) = "en") # filter for only English labels
}
}
GROUP BY ?director ?director_label
ORDER BY DESC(?rank)
LIMIT 100

query:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?event ?eventLabel ?date
WHERE
{
# find events
?event wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:occurrence].
# with a point in time or start date
OPTIONAL { ?event wdt:[property:point in time] ?date. }
OPTIONAL { ?event wdt:[property:start time] ?date. }
# but at least one of those
FILTER(BOUND(?date) && DATATYPE(?date) = xsd:dateTime).
# not in the future, and not more than 31 days ago
BIND(NOW() - ?date AS ?distance).
FILTER(0 <= ?distance && ?distance < 31).
# and get a label as well
OPTIONAL
{
?event rdfs:label ?eventLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?eventLabel) = "en").
}
}
# limit to 10 results so we don't timeout
LIMIT 10

instructions: List the authors of scientific papers who have collaborated but have Erdos numbers that don't reflect their collaboration.
What are the names of scientists who have worked together on a paper but have Erdos numbers that are not close?
Find the papers written by two authors whose Erdos numbers are more than 1 apart.
Who are the authors of scholarly articles with Erdos numbers that do not indicate they have collaborated?
Show me the scientific papers where the authors' Erdos numbers are farthest from each other.
query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
# Q#s
?paper
?author1
?author2
# title (either from title statement or label)
(IF(BOUND(?title), ?title, ?paperLabel) AS ?title)
# author labels (should be names) and their Erdos numbers
?author1Label
?erdos1
?author2Label
?erdos2
# distance between Erdos numbers
?distance
WHERE
{
# paper, instance of or subclass of scientific article; also has two authors
?paper wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:scholarly article];
wdt:[property:author] ?author1, ?author2.
# if it has a title, we'll grab that as well, but it's also okay if there's no title
OPTIONAL { ?paper wdt:[property:title] ?title. }
# grab Erdos numbers of the two authors
?author1 wdt:[property:Erdős number] ?erdos1.
?author2 wdt:[property:Erdős number] ?erdos2.
# introduce a new variable for the difference of the Erdos numbers
BIND(?erdos2 - ?erdos1 AS ?distance).
# select those cases where the distance is > 1
# (note: by *not* taking the absolute value of the distance, we avoid getting duplicated cases because the author variables might be swapped)
FILTER(?distance > 1).
# get *Label variables automagically
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}
# sort by distance first (descending), then by first author, then by second author
ORDER BY DESC(?distance) ?author1Label ?author2Label

query:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pqv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?cocktail ?cocktailLabel (GROUP_CONCAT(?ingredient; separator=", ") AS ?ingredients) # concatenate all ingredients together, separated by comma
WHERE
{
# find a cocktail
?cocktail wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:cocktail];
# get its material statement
p:[property:made from material] ?materialStat.
# get the statement value from the statement
?materialStat ps:[property:made from material] ?material.
# get the material's English label
?material rdfs:label ?materialLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?materialLabel) = "en").
# assign label to solo ingredient variable
BIND(?materialLabel AS ?ingredientSolo).
OPTIONAL {
# for some reason, we have to get the material and materialLabel again - copy+pasted from above
?materialStat ps:[property:made from material] ?material.
?material rdfs:label ?materialLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?materialLabel) = "en").
# get the quantity value from the statement (if present)
?materialStat pqv:[property:quantity] ?quantityValue.
# get the actual quantity from the quantity value
?quantityValue wikibase:quantityAmount ?quantity.
# assign quantity and material to ingredient with quantity variable
BIND(CONCAT(STR(?quantity), " ", ?materialLabel) AS ?ingredientWithQuantity).
OPTIONAL {
# same here for material and quantity
?materialStat ps:[property:made from material] ?material.
?material rdfs:label ?materialLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?materialLabel) = "en").
?materialStat pqv:[property:quantity] ?quantityValue.
?quantityValue wikibase:quantityAmount ?quantity.
# get the unit from the quantity value
?quantityValue wikibase:quantityUnit ?unit.
# throw out the unit "1" (no unit)
FILTER(?unit != wd:[entity:1]).
# get the unit's English label
?unit rdfs:label ?unitLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?unitLabel) = "en").
# assign quantity, unit, and material to ingredient with unit variable (note: we're not bothering with pluralization here, so it may sound a bit weird)
BIND(CONCAT(STR(?quantity), " ", ?unitLabel, " ", ?materialLabel) AS ?ingredientWithUnit).
}
}
# assign ingredient with unit, else ingredient with quantity, else just solo ingredient to ingredient variable
BIND(COALESCE(?ingredientWithUnit, ?ingredientWithQuantity, ?ingredientSolo) AS ?ingredient).
# get the cocktail's English label
?cocktail rdfs:label ?cocktailLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?cocktailLabel) = "en").
}
# group by cocktail
GROUP BY ?cocktail ?cocktailLabel
# show most "complicated" cocktails first
ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?ingredient))

query:
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?ratio (COUNT(?item) AS ?count) WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:painting] .
?item p:[property:height]/psv:[property:height] [
wikibase:quantityAmount ?baseHeight;
wikibase:quantityUnit [
p:[property:conversion to SI unit]/psv:[property:conversion to SI unit] [
wikibase:quantityAmount ?unitHeight;
wikibase:quantityUnit wd:[entity:metre]
]
]
].
BIND(?baseHeight * ?unitHeight AS ?height).
?item p:[property:width]/psv:[property:width] [
wikibase:quantityAmount ?baseWidth;
wikibase:quantityUnit [
p:[property:conversion to SI unit]/psv:[property:conversion to SI unit] [
wikibase:quantityAmount ?unitWidth;
wikibase:quantityUnit wd:[entity:metre]
]
]
].
BIND(?baseWidth * ?unitWidth AS ?width).
BIND(?height / ?width AS ?r) .
BIND(IF(?r<0.5,"< 0.5",
IF(?r<0.6,"0.5 - 0.6",
IF(?r<0.7,"0.6 - 0.7",
IF(?r<0.8,"0.7 - 0.8",
IF(?r<0.9,"0.8 - 0.9",
IF(?r<1.0,"0.9 - 1.0",
IF(?r<1.1,"1.0 - 1.1",
IF(?r<1.2,"1.1 - 1.2",
IF(?r<1.3,"1.2 - 1.3",
IF(?r<1.4,"1.3 - 1.4",
IF(?r<1.5,"1.4 - 1.5", "> 1.5"))))))))))) AS ?ratio) .
}
GROUP BY ?ratio
ORDER BY DESC(?count)

SELECT ?holiday ?holidayLabel WHERE {
# first get the item for today's date by stitching together the English label (month name + day number) and finding items with that label
VALUES (?monthNumber ?monthName) {
(1 "January"@en)
(2 "February"@en)
(3 "March"@en)
(4 "April"@en)
(5 "May"@en)
(6 "June"@en)
(7 "July"@en)
(8 "August"@en)
(9 "September"@en)
(10 "October"@en)
(11 "November"@en)
(12 "December"@en)
}
FILTER(?monthNumber = MONTH(NOW())).
BIND(CONCAT(?monthName, " "@en, STRLANG(STR(DAY(NOW())),"en")) AS ?dateLabel).
?date rdfs:label ?dateLabel.
# then find holidays occurring on that day
?holiday wdt:[property:day in year for periodic occurrence] ?date.
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX hint: <http://www.bigdata.com/queryHints#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
(COUNT(?page) AS ?count) ?person ?personLabel
WITH {
SELECT DISTINCT ?person WHERE {
hint:Query hint:optimizer "None".
?person wdt:[property:date of birth] ?birthdate .
BIND(MONTH(?birthdate) AS ?month)
FILTER (?month = 1)
?person p:[property:date of birth]/psv:[property:date of birth] ?timenode .
?timenode wikibase:timePrecision 11 .
VALUES ?year { 1956 1960 1964 1968 1972 1976 1980 1984 1988 1992 1996 2004 2008 }
BIND(YEAR(?birthdate) AS ?year)
}
LIMIT 1000000
} AS %persons
WHERE {
INCLUDE %persons
?page schema:about ?person .
?person wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
GROUP BY ?person ?personLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?count)
LIMIT 200

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?band ?bandLabel (AVG(?age) AS ?avgAge) WHERE {
?band wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:musical group] .
?band (p:[property:location of formation]/ps:[property:location of formation]/p:[property:country]/ps:[property:country])|(p:[property:country of origin]/ps:[property:country of origin]) wd:[entity:United Kingdom] . # country of inception / country of origin; [entity:United Kingdom] is UK
?band p:[property:has part(s)] ?ms .
?ms ps:[property:has part(s)] ?member .
FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?ms pq:[property:end time] [] } .
?member p:[property:date of birth]/ps:[property:date of birth] ?dob .
BIND (YEAR(NOW()) - YEAR(?dob) AS ?age)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
GROUP BY ?band ?bandLabel
HAVING (AVG(?age) >= 70 && COUNT(?age) > 1)
ORDER BY DESC(?avgAge)

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription ?start ?end ?daysThere ?daysGone ?dateWhereDaysThereEqualsDaysGone WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:inception] ?start;
wdt:[property:dissolved, abolished or demolished date] ?end.
BIND(?end - ?start AS ?daysThere)
BIND(FLOOR(NOW() - ?end) AS ?daysGone)
FILTER(?daysThere > 0) # T186452
BIND(?end + STRDT(CONCAT("P", xsd:string(xsd:integer(?daysThere)), "D"), xsd:duration) AS ?dateWhereDaysThereEqualsDaysGone)
FILTER(YEAR(?dateWhereDaysThereEqualsDaysGone) = YEAR(NOW()) && MONTH(?dateWhereDaysThereEqualsDaysGone) = MONTH(NOW()))
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?dateWhereDaysThereEqualsDaysGone

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
?book ?bookLabel
?kilogram ?weight ?unit ?unitLabel
WITH {
SELECT * WHERE {
?book wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:version, edition or translation] .
?book p:[property:mass] / psv:[property:mass] ?weight_value .
?weight_value wikibase:quantityAmount ?weight .
?weight_value wikibase:quantityUnit ?unit .
?unit wdt:[property:conversion to SI unit] ?factor .
BIND(?weight * ?factor AS ?kilogram)
}
} AS %results
WHERE {
INCLUDE %results
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?kilogram

SELECT ?city ?cityLabel ?coord ?ratioBin ?rgb
WHERE
{
BIND(
IF(?ratio < 2, "< 2",
IF(?ratio < 3, "[2;3)",
IF(?ratio < 4, "[3;4)",
IF(?ratio < 5, "[4;5)",
"5+"))))
AS ?ratioBin)

IF(?ratio < 2, "0072E5",
IF(?ratio < 3, "2F58AB",
IF(?ratio < 4, "5F3F72",
IF(?ratio < 5, "8F2539",
"BF0C00"))))

{
SELECT ?city ?coord (count(?item)*10000/?pop as ?ratio)
WHERE
{
?item wdt:[property:Italian School ID] ?id .

?item wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity] ?city .
?city wdt:[property:population] ?pop .
?city wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord .
# ?city wdt:[property:capital of] ?place.
# ?place wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:province of Italy].

group by ?city ?pop ?coord
having (?pop >= 5000)

}
}

(SAMPLE(?x) AS ?x) (SAMPLE(?layer) AS ?layer) WHERE {
{ ?x wdt:[property:part of] wd:[entity:Welsh Journals]. }
UNION
{ ?x wdt:[property:part of] wd:[entity:Welsh Newspapers Online] . }

wdt:[property:place of publication] ?place .

BIND(FLOOR(?year / 10) *10 as ?decade )
BIND(
IF(?decade =1770, "1770s",
IF(?decade =1780, "1780s",
IF(?decade =1790, "1790s",
IF(?decade =1800, "1800s",
IF(?decade =1810, "1810s",

IF(?decade =1840, "1840s",

IF(?decade =1860, "1860s",
IF(?decade =1870, "1870s",
IF(?decade =1880, "1880s",
IF(?decade =1890, "1890s",
IF(?decade =1900, "1900s",
IF(?decade =1910, "1910s",
IF(?decade =1920, "1920s",
IF(?decade =1930, "1930s",
IF(?decade =1940, "1940s",
IF(?decade =1950, "1950s",
IF(?decade =1960, "1960s",
IF(?decade =1970, "1970s",
IF(?decade =1980, "1980s",
IF(?decade =1990, "1990s",
" "))))))))))))))))))))))) AS ?layer).
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}
GROUP BY ?decade ?place ?placeLabel ?coord ?year ?xLabel ?image
ORDER BY ?decade

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?img ?bbox WHERE {
?class wdt:[property:collection] wd:[entity:King George III Topographical Collection] . # KTop
?class wdt:[property:main subject] wd:[entity:South America] .
?item wdt:[property:collection] ?class .
?class wdt:[property:main subject] wd:[entity:South America] .
?item p:[property:coordinates of northernmost point]/psv:[property:coordinates of northernmost point]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?nth .
?item p:[property:coordinates of southernmost point]/psv:[property:coordinates of southernmost point]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?sth .
?item p:[property:coordinates of easternmost point]/psv:[property:coordinates of easternmost point]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?east .
?item p:[property:coordinates of westernmost point]/psv:[property:coordinates of westernmost point]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?west .
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:image] ?img} .
BIND(STRDT( CONCAT('LINESTRING (',
str(?west), ' ', str(?sth), ',',
str(?west), ' ', str(?nth), ',',
str(?east), ' ', str(?nth), ',',
str(?east), ' ', str(?sth), ',',
str(?west), ' ', str(?sth), ')' ), geo:wktLiteral) AS ?bbox) .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?mountain ?mountainLabel (sample(?height) as ?height) (year(?date) as ?year) (sample(?location) as ?location) ?layer
WHERE
{
?mountain wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:mountain] . # Everything that's a mountain
?mountain wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?location . # and has a coordinate
?mountain p:[property:elevation above sea level] ?heightstatement . # and has a height-statement
?heightstatement psv:[property:elevation above sea level] ?PSVStatement. # normalised height statement
?PSVStatement wikibase:quantityNormalized ?another_statement .
?another_statement wikibase:quantityAmount ?height.# height - phew!
FILTER(?height > 6000) # only the tallest
OPTIONAL {
?mountain p:[property:significant event] ?event . # and within that "significant event" statement
?event ps:[property:significant event] wd:[entity:first ascent] . # continued...
?event pq:[property:point in time] ?date . #it has a "point in time" qualifier statement.
bind ("Climbed" as ?layer) # this seems to be what we need to get colour labels -
# ie if it falls in the optional group of "was first summited"
# then bind to a new layer, otherwise no special layer
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
group by ?mountain ?mountainLabel ?date ?layer
ORDER BY DESC (?height)
LIMIT 200

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?label ?coord ?rgb WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:Italy].

?item rdfs:label ?labelWithLanguage.

BIND(
IF(STRENDS(?labelWithLanguage, "ago"), "CC3333",
IF(STRENDS(?labelWithLanguage, "ate"), "33AACC",

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?itemLabel (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?counLabel; SEPARATOR=", ") AS ?country) (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?hqLabel; SEPARATOR=", ") AS ?headquarters) ?revenue ?revenue_USD ?unitLabel ?date
WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:business].
?item p:[property:total revenue] ?statement.
OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:[property:headquarters location] ?hq. }
OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:[property:country] ?coun. }
?statement wikibase:rank ?rank.
OPTIONAL {
?item p:[property:total revenue] ?statement1.
?statement1 wikibase:rank wikibase:PreferredRank.
FILTER(?rank != wikibase:PreferredRank)
FILTER(?statement1 != ?statement)
}
OPTIONAL { ?statement pq:[property:point in time] ?date. }
{
?statement psv:[property:total revenue] _:b9.
_:b9 wikibase:quantityAmount ?revenue.
_:b9 wikibase:quantityUnit wd:[entity:United States dollar].
BIND(wd:[entity:United States dollar] AS ?unit)
BIND(?revenue AS ?revenue_USD)
}
UNION
{
?statement psv:[property:total revenue] _:b10.
_:b10 wikibase:quantityAmount ?revenue.
_:b10 wikibase:quantityUnit ?unit.
?unit p:[property:price] ?unit_statement.
?unit_statement wikibase:rank ?unit_rank.
?unit_statement psv:[property:price] _:b11.
_:b11 wikibase:quantityUnit wd:[entity:United States dollar].
_:b11 wikibase:quantityAmount ?usd.
OPTIONAL {
?unit p:[property:price] ?unit_statement1.
?unit_statement1 (psv:[property:price]/wikibase:quantityUnit) wd:[entity:United States dollar].
?unit_statement1 wikibase:rank wikibase:PreferredRank.
FILTER(?unit_rank != wikibase:PreferredRank)
FILTER(?unit_statement1 != ?unit_statement)
}
BIND(?revenue * ?usd AS ?revenue_USD)
FILTER(?unit != wd:[entity:United States dollar])
FILTER(?unit_rank != wikibase:DeprecatedRank)
FILTER(!BOUND(?unit_statement1))
}
SERVICE wikibase:label {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en" .
?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel .
?coun rdfs:label ?counLabel .
?hq rdfs:label ?hqLabel .
?unit rdfs:label ?unitLabel .
}
FILTER(?rank != wikibase:DeprecatedRank)
FILTER(!BOUND(?statement1))
}
GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?revenue ?revenue_USD ?unitLabel ?date
ORDER BY DESC(?revenue_USD)
LIMIT 15

?countryB wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:country] .

hint:Query hint:optimizer "None".
# get metro stations in germany
?station wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:metro station] ;
wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:Germany] .

?station wdt:[property:image] ?picture .
# build commons urls
BIND(STRAFTER(str(?picture), "Special:FilePath/") AS ?filename)
BIND(wikibase:decodeUri(CONCAT("File:", ?filename)) AS ?file)
# and ask commons for the categories the pictures are in
SERVICE wikibase:mwapi {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:api "Categories".
bd:serviceParam wikibase:endpoint "commons.wikipedia.org".
bd:serviceParam mwapi:titles ?file.
?pictureCategory wikibase:apiOutput mwapi:category.
}
# and only get those with a Public Domain category
FILTER(STRSTARTS(?pictureCategory, "Category:PD-"))
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "de,[AUTO_LANGUAGE]". }
}
GROUP BY ?station ?stationLabel ?picture
LIMIT 100

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?when (YEAR(?when) as ?date) ?pic

SELECT
?person
?personLabel
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?myRanklabel;separator=', ') as ?myRanklabel)
?image
(COUNT(DISTINCT ?languageArticle) as ?languageArticleCount)
WHERE {
?person wdt:[property:member of] wd:[entity:Starfleet] .
OPTIONAL {
?person wdt:[property:military rank] ?rank .

?languageArticle schema:about ?person

}

?person ?personLabel ?rankLabel ?image

DESC(?languageArticleCount)

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?church ?churchLabel ?churchloc ?dist ?other ?otherLabel
WHERE
{
?church wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:church building] . # this thing is a church
?church wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:United Kingdom] . # and it's in the UK
?church wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?churchloc . # and it has a location
?other wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:church building] . # another thing is also a church
SERVICE wikibase:around {
?other wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?otherloc .
bd:serviceParam wikibase:center ?churchloc .
bd:serviceParam wikibase:radius "0.025" . # and is pretty much exactly on the same spot (+-25m)
}
FILTER (STR(?church) > STR(?other)) # filter so each pair only shows up once
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en" }
BIND(geof:distance(?churchloc, ?otherloc) as ?dist)
}
ORDER BY ?dist

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

# 57=director 58=screenwriter 86=composer 161=cast member 162=producer 344=photography 1431=executive producer
?cast wdt:[property:country of citizenship] wd:[entity:United States of America] .
?cast wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dob .

bind( 1000+year(?date)-year(?dob) as ?age_num )
bind( SUBSTR(str(?age_num),1,4) as ?age )
FILTER(BOUND(?age_num))
FILTER(?age_num<=1100)
FILTER(?age_num>=1000)
FILTER(year(?date)>2000)
#FILTER(year(?date)<2010)
}
GROUP BY ?genderLabel ?age
#ORDER BY ?genderLabel ?age

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?saint (COUNT(?item) AS ?count) WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:commune of France] .
?item rdfs:label ?itemL filter (lang(?itemL) = "fr") .
FILTER regex(?itemL, "^saint-", "i")
BIND (REPLACE(STRAFTER(?itemL, "Saint-"), "-.*$", "", "i") AS ?saint)
}
GROUP BY ?saint
HAVING (?count >= 3)

instructions: What is the number of disasters that occurred on a specific date?
List all the days of the week with their corresponding disaster counts.

How many disasters happened on Mondays, Tuesdays, ..., Sundays?

query:
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT (?q AS ?Date) (SUM(?mon) AS ?Mon) (SUM(?tue) AS ?Tue) (SUM(?wed) AS ?Wed) (SUM(?thu) AS ?Thu) (SUM(?fri) AS ?Fri) (SUM(?sat) AS ?Sat) (SUM(?sun) AS ?Sun) (COUNT(?start_time) AS ?Tot) WHERE {
{
?disaster wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:disaster] ;
p:[property:start time] ?start_time_stm . # find the date multi-day disasters started
?start_time_stm ps:[property:start time] ?start_time .
?start_time_stm psv:[property:start time] ?start_time_node .
?start_time_node wikibase:timePrecision ?tp . FILTER(?tp=11)
}
UNION
{
?disaster wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:disaster] ;
p:[property:point in time] ?start_time_stm . # find all those which have "point in time" (ie one-day events)
?start_time_stm ps:[property:point in time] ?start_time .
?start_time_stm psv:[property:point in time] ?start_time_node .
?start_time_node wikibase:timePrecision ?tp . FILTER(?tp=11)
}
# this beautiful bit of code finds all the relevant days of the week
# using https://cs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algoritmus_pro_v%C3%BDpo%C4%8Det_dne_v_t%C3%BDdnu#Zeller%C5%AFv_algoritmus
BIND( DAY( ?start_time ) AS ?q ) .
BIND( MONTH( ?start_time ) + IF( MONTH( ?start_time ) < 3, 12, 0 ) AS ?m ) .
BIND( YEAR( ?start_time ) - IF( MONTH( ?start_time ) < 3, 1, 0 ) AS ?_year ) .
BIND( ?_year - FLOOR( ?_year / 100 ) * 100 AS ?K ) . # modulo
BIND( FLOOR( YEAR( ?start_time ) / 100 ) AS ?J ) .
BIND( ?q + FLOOR( 13 * ( ?m + 1 ) / 5 ) + ?K + FLOOR( ?K / 4 ) + FLOOR( ?J / 4 ) - 2 * ?J AS ?_h ) .
BIND( ?_h - FLOOR( ?_h / 7 ) * 7 AS ?weekday) . # modulo, 0 is Saturday
BIND(IF(?weekday=2,1,0) AS ?mon)
BIND(IF(?weekday=3,1,0) AS ?tue)
BIND(IF(?weekday=4,1,0) AS ?wed)
BIND(IF(?weekday=5,1,0) AS ?thu)
BIND(IF(?weekday=6,1,0) AS ?fri)
BIND(IF(?weekday=0,1,0) AS ?sat)
BIND(IF(?weekday=1,1,0) AS ?sun)
}
GROUP BY ?q
ORDER BY ?Date

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?vLabel ?pop {
?v wdt:[property:instance of] wd:Q13005188 .
?v wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]* wd:[entity:West Godavari district].
?v p:[property:female population] ?fps11. ?fps11 ps:[property:female population] ?fp11. ?fps11 pq:[property:point in time] ?fp11d. FILTER(year(?fp11d) = 2011).
?v p:[property:female population] ?fps01. ?fps01 ps:[property:female population] ?fp01. ?fps01 pq:[property:point in time] ?fp01d. FILTER(year(?fp01d) = 2001).
?v p:[property:male population] ?mps11. ?mps11 ps:[property:male population] ?mp11. ?mps11 pq:[property:point in time] ?mp11d. FILTER(year(?mp11d) = 2011).
?v p:[property:male population] ?mps01. ?mps01 ps:[property:male population] ?mp01. ?mps01 pq:[property:point in time] ?mp01d. FILTER(year(?mp01d) = 2001).
BIND((xsd:integer(?mp11)/xsd:integer(?fp11)) - (xsd:integer(?mp01)/xsd:integer(?fp01)) as ?change)
BIND(IF(?change < 0, -1 * ?change, 0) as ?pop).
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "te,en" }
}
GROUP BY ?pop ?vLabel

#

WHERE {
hint:Query hint:optimizer "None".
?lexeme dct:language wd:[entity:Danish] .
?lexeme ontolex:lexicalForm ?form .

select distinct ?item ?itemLabel ?twitter1 ?twitter2 ?facebook1 ?facebook2 where
{
{ ?item wdt:[property:Twitter (X) username] ?twitter1 . ?item wdt:[property:Twitter (X) username] ?twitter2 .
filter(?twitter1 > ?twitter2) .
# item has two values for twitter account
filter((lcase(?twitter1)) = (lcase(?twitter2)) ) . }
# but they are the same case-insensitive text
union
{ ?item wdt:[property:Facebook username] ?facebook1 . ?item wdt:[property:Facebook username] ?facebook2 .
filter(?facebook1 > ?facebook2) .
filter((lcase(?facebook1)) = (lcase(?facebook2)) ) . }

# as of 2019-03-19, 176 Twitter and 27 Facebook
# nb please do *not* fix automatically by removing entries without checking them first
# as one value may have key qualifiers (follower count, verification, sources, etc)!
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?sort ?item ?itemLabel ?article
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?occ_label; SEPARATOR = ' / ') AS ?occs)
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?field_label; SEPARATOR = ' / ') AS ?fields)
?dob ?dod
WHERE {
wd:[entity:engineer] ^wdt:[property:subclass of]* ?occ .
FILTER (?occ != wd:[entity:record producer]) .
?occ ^wdt:[property:occupation] ?item .
?item wdt:[property:sex or gender] wd:[entity:female] .
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] .
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dob} .
BIND(COALESCE (year(?dob), 9999) AS ?sort) .
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:date of death] ?dod} .
FILTER (!bound(?dod) || !(year(?dod) < 1919)).
VALUES ?uk {wd:[entity:United Kingdom] wd:[entity:United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland]}
?item wdt:[property:country of citizenship]|((wdt:[property:work location]|wdt:[property:place of birth]|wdt:[property:place of death])/wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]*) ?uk .
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:field of work] ?field .
OPTIONAL {?field rdfs:label ?field_label. FILTER(lang(?field_label) = 'en') } .
}
OPTIONAL {?occ rdfs:label ?occ_label. FILTER(lang(?occ_label) = 'en') } .
OPTIONAL {?article schema:about ?item . ?article schema:isPartOf <https://en.wikipedia.org/> } .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?article ?dob ?sort ?dod
ORDER BY ?sort ?itemLabel

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

select distinct ?item ?itemLabel ?leadership_start_time (MAX(?elec_date) AS ?elec_date) (MIN(?days) AS ?days)
with {
select ?elec ?elec_date WHERE {
?elec wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:United Kingdom general election] .
?elec wdt:[property:point in time] ?elec_date .
}
} AS %elections
where {
hint:Query hint:optimizer "None".
?role wdt:[property:subclass of]? wd:[entity:party leader] .
?pos_stmt ps:[property:position held] ?role .
?pos_stmt pq:[property:start time] ?leadership_start_time .
FILTER (year(?leadership_start_time) > 1945) .
MINUS {?role p:[property:subclass of]/pq:[property:of]/wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:parliamentary group]} .
?item p:[property:position held] ?pos_stmt .
?item wdt:[property:position held]/wdt:[property:subclass of] wd:[entity:Member of Parliament] .
INCLUDE %elections .
FILTER (?elec_date < ?leadership_start_time).
BIND ((?leadership_start_time - ?elec_date) AS ?days)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". } .
} GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?leadership_start_time
ORDER BY DESC(?days)

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?mp ?mpLabel ?image ?pob ?pobLabel ?pobCoords ?con ?conLabel ?conCoords ?line ?rgb ?layer WHERE {
$mp wdt:[property:place of birth] ?pob .
OPTIONAL { ?mp wdt:[property:image] ?image .}
?pob wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?pobCoords .
?pob p:[property:coordinate location] [ ps:[property:coordinate location] []; psv:[property:coordinate location] [ wikibase:geoLongitude ?poblon; wikibase:geoLatitude ?poblat; ] ].
$mp p:[property:position held] ?mpstmt .
?mpstmt ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:member of the 57th Parliament of the United Kingdom] .
?mpstmt pq:[property:electoral district] ?con .
?con wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?conCoords .
?con p:[property:coordinate location] [
ps:[property:coordinate location] [];
psv:[property:coordinate location] [
wikibase:geoLongitude ?conlon;
wikibase:geoLatitude ?conlat;
]
].
MINUS {?mpstmt pq:[property:end time] ?e }
?mpstmt pq:[property:parliamentary group] ?party .
?party wdt:[property:sRGB color hex triplet] ?rgb .
?party rdfs:label ?layer .
FILTER (LANG(?layer) = "en")
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING (', STR(?poblon), ' ', STR(?poblat), ',', STR(?conlon), ' ', STR(?conlat), ')') AS ?str) .
BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

?l a ontolex:LexicalEntry;
dct:language ?language.
?language wdt:[property:ISO 639-1 code] 'sv'.

}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?cd ?l ?i ?iLabel ?ct ?ctLabel ?rgb ?x WITH{SELECT ?i ?cd ?lat1 ?lon1 ?x(sample(?op)as?op)WHERE{{?i wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:airport]}UNION{?i wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:international airport]}?i wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?cd;wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:India];p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location] ?y.?y wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1;wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1.OPTIONAL{?i wdt:[property:operator] ?op}}GROUP BY ?i ?cd ?lat1 ?lon1 ?x}AS%s
WITH{SELECT ?l ?o ?t WHERE{INCLUDE %s.?i wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:India];p:[property:scheduled service destination] ?nss.?nss ps:[property:scheduled service destination] ?ns.?ns wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:India];p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location] ?z.?z wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2;wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2.OPTIONAL{?nss pq:[property:operator] ?o}FILTER(STR(?i)< STR(?ns)).BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING(',STR(?lon1),' ',STR(?lat1),',',STR(?lon2),' ',STR(?lat2),')')AS?str).BIND(STRDT(?str,geo:wktLiteral)AS?l)}}AS%l
WHERE{{INCLUDE%s}UNION{INCLUDE%l}.BIND(IF(BOUND(?l),"f0f","007f00") as ?rgb)SERVICE wikibase:label{bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en".}}#

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?pLabel ?sideLabel ?shape ?rgb WHERE {
OPTIONAL { ?p wdt:[property:driving side] ?side } # driving side
OPTIONAL { ?p wdt:[property:geoshape] ?shape } # geoshape

IF(?side = wd:[entity:right], "0066B4", 1/0), # blue

}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

SELECT (REPLACE(REPLACE(?nobelPrizeLabel_, "^Nobel Prize in ", ""), "^Nobel (.*) Prize$", "$1") AS ?nobelPrizeLabel) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?winner) AS ?winners) (COALESCE(?genderLabel_, "N/A"@en) AS ?genderLabel) WHERE {

ps:[property:award received] ?nobelPrize;

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

SELECT ?d ?dLabel ?shape ?ratio ?rgb WHERE {
?d wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:district of India]; p:[property:literate population] ?litpopstmt ; p:[property:illiterate population] ?illitpopstmt ; wdt:[property:geoshape] ?shape.

BIND(xsd:integer(?illitpop)/xsd:integer(?litpop) AS ?ratio)

SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX ontolex: <http://www.w3.org/ns/lemon/ontolex#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?firstLetter (COUNT(?form) AS ?count ) WHERE {
?lexeme a ontolex:LexicalEntry ; dct:language ?language ; ontolex:lexicalForm ?form .

SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

#defaultView:Graph
SELECT DISTINCT ?cited_country ?cited_countryLabel ?cited_flag ?citing_country ?citing_countryLabel ?citing_flag
WITH {
  SELECT DISTINCT ?cited_country ?citing_country (COUNT(?citing_country) AS ?count)
                                  WHERE {
    ?citing_work wdt:[property:author] ?citing_author . 
    ?citing_work wdt:[property:main subject] wd:[entity:COVID-19] . # Replace [entity:COVID-19] (COVID-19)with Wikidata ID of your concept of interest, e.g. Q202864 (Zika virus) 
    ?cited_work wdt:[property:main subject] wd:[entity:COVID-19]: . # Replace [entity:COVID-19] (COVID-19)with Wikidata ID of your concept of interest, e.g. Q202864 (Zika virus) 
    ?citing_work wdt:[property:cites work] ?cited_work . 
    ?cited_work wdt:[property:author] ?cited_author .  
    FILTER (?citing_work != ?cited_work)
    FILTER NOT EXISTS {
      ?citing_work wdt:[property:author] ?author .
      ?citing_work wdt:[property:cites work] ?cited_work .
      ?cited_work  wdt:[property:author] ?author .
    }
    ?citing_author (wdt:[property:employer]|wdt:[property:affiliation]) ?citing_organization . 
    ?cited_author (wdt:[property:employer]|wdt:[property:affiliation]) ?cited_organization . 
    ?cited_organization wdt:[property:country] ?cited_country.
    ?citing_organization wdt:[property:country] ?citing_country.
    FILTER (?citing_country != ?cited_country)
  }
  GROUP BY ?cited_country ?citing_country
  ORDER BY DESC(?count)
  LIMIT 30 # Adjust number of connections to display
} AS %results
WHERE {
  INCLUDE %results
  ?cited_country wdt:[property:flag] / wdt:[property:image] ?cited_flag . 
  ?citing_country wdt:[property:flag] / wdt:[property:image] ?citing_flag . 
 SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
 }

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?country ?countryLabel ?daysInUN (SUM(?daysInOffice) AS ?daysKnown) ((100* ?daysKnown / ?daysInUN) AS ?filledPercent) WHERE {
# Current UN Member States
?country wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:sovereign state] ; p:[property:member of] ?ms .
?ms ps:[property:member of] wd:[entity:United Nations] ; pq:[property:start time] ?joined .
FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?ms pq:[property:end time] [] }
BIND(FLOOR(NOW()-?joined) AS ?daysInUN)
# what office(s) = head of government, and when?
?country p:[property:office held by head of government] ?os .
?os ps:[property:office held by head of government] ?office .
OPTIONAL { ?os pq:[property:start time] ?officeStart }
OPTIONAL { ?os pq:[property:end time] ?officeEnd }
FILTER ( !BOUND(?officeEnd) || (?officeEnd > ?joined) )
# Who has held office in that period?
BIND(IF(BOUND(?officeStart), IF(?officeStart < ?joined, ?joined, ?officeStart), ?joined) AS ?effectiveStart)
BIND(IF(BOUND(?officeEnd), ?officeEnd, NOW()) AS ?effectiveEnd)
?person wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] ; p:[property:position held] ?ps .
?ps ps:[property:position held] ?office ; pq:[property:start time] ?heldStart .
OPTIONAL { ?ps pq:[property:end time] ?heldEnd }
FILTER ( !BOUND(?heldEnd) || (?heldEnd > ?effectiveStart) )
BIND(IF(BOUND(?heldEnd), ?heldEnd, NOW()) AS ?heldPeriodEnd)
BIND(IF(?heldStart < ?effectiveStart, ?effectiveStart, ?heldStart) AS ?heldPeriodStart)
BIND(FLOOR(?heldPeriodEnd - ?heldPeriodStart) AS ?daysInOffice)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
GROUP BY ?country ?countryLabel ?daysInUN
ORDER BY DESC(?filledPercent) ?countryLabel

instructions: Find the list of mountains in Austria along with their heights and coordinates.
Retrieve the data of mountains in Austria, including their names, heights, and geographical coordinates.
Can you show me the information about mountains in Austria, including their names, heights, and coordinates?
I need to see the details of mountains in Austria, including their names, heights, and coordinates.
Pull up the data of mountains in Austria, including their names, heights, and geographical coordinates.
query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?x ?xLabel ?description ?x_coords ?rgb WITH {
# extract the data
SELECT ?data ?x ?x_coords WHERE {
?x wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:mountain] .
?x p:[property:elevation above sea level]/psn:[property:elevation above sea level] [
wikibase:quantityAmount ?data
] .
?x wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:Austria] .
?x wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?x_coords .
}
} AS %totals
# determine the max and min values (used to calculate the spread
WITH {
SELECT (MAX(?data) AS ?max_data) (MIN(?data) AS ?min_data) WHERE {
INCLUDE %totals
}} AS %min_max
WHERE {
INCLUDE %totals
INCLUDE %min_max
?x rdfs:label ?xLabel. FILTER (LANG(?xLabel) = "en") .
BIND (CONCAT("The height of ", ?xLabel, " is about ", STR(ROUND(?data)), " metres" ) AS ?description)
BIND ( ?max_data - ?min_data AS ?spread )
BIND ( xsd:integer( 100 * (?data - ?min_data) / ?spread) AS ?percent ) # 0 -> 100
# some example hues 0:red, 20:orange, 50:yellow, 90:green, 180:cyan, 220:blue, 280:indigo, 330:violet, 340:red
# varying hue
# BIND ( 255 * ?percent / 100 + 0 AS ?hue )
# BIND (1 AS ?value) #
# BIND (1 AS ?saturation) . # 0 -> 1
# varying the hue's value
BIND ( (1 - ?percent / 100 + 0) AS ?value ) # to black
BIND ( 255 * ?percent / 100 + 0 AS ?hue )
BIND (1 AS ?saturation) . # 0 -> 1
# varying the hue's saturation
# BIND ( (1 - ?percent / 100 + 0) AS ?saturation ) # to -> white
# BIND (0 AS ?hue) # red
# BIND (1 AS ?value) . # 0 -> 1
# the following algorithm based on https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3018313/algorithm-to-convert-rgb-to-hsv-and-hsv-to-rgb-in-range-0-255-for-both
BIND ( ?hue / 60 AS ?hh )
BIND ( FLOOR (?hh) AS ?i ) .
BIND ( ?hh - ?i AS ?ff) .
BIND ( ?value * ( 1 - ?saturation ) AS ?p) .
BIND ( ?value * ( 1 - ( ?saturation * ?ff)) AS ?q ) .
BIND ( ?value * ( 1 - ( ?saturation * (1 - ?ff ))) AS ?t ) .
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?i = 0, ?value, 1/0),
IF(?i = 1, ?q, 1/0),
IF(?i = 2, ?p, 1/0),
IF(?i = 3, ?p, 1/0),
IF(?i = 4, ?t, 1/0),
IF(?i = 5, ?value, 1/0),
?value
) AS ?r )
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?i = 0, ?t, 1/0),
IF(?i = 1, ?value, 1/0),
IF(?i = 2, ?value, 1/0),
IF(?i = 3, ?q, 1/0),
IF(?i = 4, ?p, 1/0),
IF(?i = 5, ?p, 1/0),
?p
) AS ?g )
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?i = 0, ?p, 1/0),
IF(?i = 1, ?p, 1/0),
IF(?i = 2, ?t, 1/0),
IF(?i = 3, ?value, 1/0),
IF(?i = 4, ?value, 1/0),
IF(?i = 5, ?q, 1/0),
?q
) AS ?b )
BIND (FLOOR(255 * ?r) AS ?red)
BIND (FLOOR(255 * ?g) AS ?green)
BIND (FLOOR(255 * ?b) AS ?blue)
# red
BIND ( FLOOR (?red / 16) AS ?red_1 )
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?red_1 < 10, STR(?red_1), 1/0),
IF(?red_1 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?red_1 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?red_1 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?red_1 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?red_1 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?red_1 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?red_hex1 )
BIND (FLOOR(?red - (16 * xsd:integer( ?red / 16 ))) AS ?red_2)
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?red_2 < 10, STR(?red_2), 1/0),
IF(?red_2 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?red_2 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?red_2 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?red_2 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?red_2 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?red_2 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?red_hex2 )
BIND (CONCAT(STR(?red_hex1), STR(?red_hex2)) AS ?red_hex )
# green
BIND ( FLOOR (?green / 16) AS ?green_1 )
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?green_1 < 10, STR(?green_1), 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?green_hex1 )
BIND (FLOOR(?green - (16 * xsd:integer( ?green / 16 ))) AS ?green_2)
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?green_2 < 10, STR(?green_2), 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?green_hex2 )
BIND (CONCAT(STR(?green_hex1), STR(?green_hex2)) AS ?green_hex )
# blue
BIND ( FLOOR (?blue / 16) AS ?blue_1 )
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?blue_1 < 10, STR(?blue_1), 1/0),
IF(?blue_1 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?blue_1 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?blue_1 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?blue_1 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?blue_1 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?blue_1 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?blue_hex1 )
BIND (FLOOR(?blue - (16 * xsd:integer( ?blue / 16 ))) AS ?blue_2)
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?blue_2 < 10, STR(?blue_2), 1/0),
IF(?blue_2 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?blue_2 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?blue_2 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?blue_2 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?blue_2 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?blue_2 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?blue_hex2 )
BIND (CONCAT(STR(?blue_hex1), STR(?blue_hex2)) AS ?blue_hex )
BIND (CONCAT(STR(?red_hex), STR(?green_hex), STR(?blue_hex)) AS ?rgb)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

SELECT ?languageLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?l) AS ?count) WHERE {
?l a ontolex:LexicalEntry ; ontolex:lexicalForm ?form ; dct:language ?language .

}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?geo ?causes ?countryLabel ?rgb ?population (CONCAT(str(year(?datum)),"-",CONCAT(IF(month(?datum)<10,"0",""),str(month(?datum))),"-",CONCAT(IF(day(?datum)<10,"0",""),str(day(?datum)))) AS ?when) {
?item wdt:[property:facet of] wd:[entity:COVID-19 pandemic] .
?item wdt:[property:country] ?country .
?country wdt:[property:population] ?pop.
?country wdt:[property:geoshape] ?geo .
MINUS { ?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:timeline] . }
OPTIONAL { ?item p:[property:number of cases] ?p1603stm .
?p1603stm ps:[property:number of cases] ?nr_causes .
?p1603stm wikibase:rank ?rank . FILTER(?rank=wikibase:PreferredRank)
OPTIONAL{?p1603stm pq:[property:point in time] ?datum }
}
BIND(IF(?nr_causes>=100,'FF0000',IF(?nr_causes>=10,'FF3333',IF(?nr_causes>=5,'FF6666',IF(?nr_causes>=2,'FF9999',IF(?nr_causes>0,'FFCCCC','FFFFFF'))))) AS ?rgb)
BIND(CONCAT("Number of cases coronavirus reported: ", str(?nr_causes)) AS ?causes)
BIND((round(?pop/100000)/10) AS ?popM )
BIND(CONCAT("Population (million): ", str(round(?popM))) AS ?population)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?artistName ?albumTitle ?releaseDate
WHERE {
?artist wdt:[property:genre] wd:[entity:electronic dance music] ; # artist has genre of EDM
rdfs:label ?artistName .
FILTER ( lang(?artistName) = "en" )
?album wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:album] .
?album wdt:[property:performer] ?artist ; # album has performer
rdfs:label ?albumTitle ;
p:[property:publication date] ?releaseDateThing .# release date as (claim about the date?)
?releaseDateThing ps:[property:publication date] ?releaseDate . # release date as ISO 8601
FILTER (?releaseDate < "1980-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
FILTER ( lang(?albumTitle) = "en" )
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pqv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/value/>
PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?date ?count ?measureLabel
WHERE {
BIND(wd:[entity:COVID-19 pandemic] AS ?outbreak).
{
BIND(wd:[entity:infection] AS ?measure).
?outbreak p:[property:number of cases] ?cases.
?cases prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:[property:stated in]/wdt:[property:author] wd:[entity:World Health Organization].
?cases pqv:[property:point in time]/wikibase:timeValue ?date.
?cases psv:[property:number of cases]/wikibase:quantityAmount ?count.
?cases psv:[property:number of cases]/wikibase:quantityAmount ?infection_count.
} UNION {
BIND(wd:[entity:death] AS ?measure).
?outbreak p:[property:number of deaths] ?deaths.
?deaths prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:[property:stated in]/wdt:[property:author] wd:[entity:World Health Organization].
?deaths pqv:[property:point in time]/wikibase:timeValue ?date.
?deaths psv:[property:number of deaths]/wikibase:quantityAmount ?count.
?deaths psv:[property:number of deaths]/wikibase:quantityAmount ?death_count.
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ASC(?date) DESC(?measure)

query:
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT (SAMPLE(?date) AS ?date) (SUM(?count) AS ?cumulative_count) ?milestone
{
{ SELECT ?qid_rounded (count(?item) AS ?count) WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:given name] wd:[entity:John] .
BIND( xsd:integer( substr(str(?item), 33)) as ?qid)
BIND(xsd:integer(?qid/50000) as ?qid_cut)
BIND(?qid_cut*50000 as ?qid_rounded)
}
GROUP BY ?qid_rounded
}
wd:[entity:QID milestone] p:[property:quantity] ?milestonep .
?milestonep ps:[property:quantity] ?milestone .
FILTER(?milestone > ?qid_rounded) .
?milestonep pq:[property:point in time] ?date .
}
GROUP BY ?milestone

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?start ?end ?child ?childLabel (MAX(?child_dob) AS ?child_dob1) (MIN(?child_age) AS ?child_age1) WHERE {
?item p:[property:position held] ?pm_stmt .
?pm_stmt ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:Prime Minister of the United Kingdom] .
?pm_stmt pq:[property:start time] ?start .
OPTIONAL {?pm_stmt pq:[property:end time] ?end} .
?item wdt:[property:child] ?child .
?child wdt:[property:date of birth] ?child_dob .
FILTER(! (?child_dob > ?end)) .
BIND (((?start - ?child_dob) / 365.24) AS ?child_age) .
FILTER (?child_age < 5)
FILTER NOT EXISTS {
?child wdt:[property:date of death] ?child_dod .
FILTER (?child_dod < ?start) .
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?start ?end ?child ?childLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?start) ?child_dob1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?countryLabel (STR(YEAR(?date)) AS ?year) ?title WHERE {
#getting award winners for each year
?item p:[property:award received] ?st1; wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:film]. ?st1 ps:[property:award received] wd:[entity:European Film Award for Best Film]; pq:[property:point in time] ?date.
#making sure the statement is sourced with a page from the domain "www.europeanfilmacademy.org"
?st1 prov:wasDerivedFrom ?ref1.
?ref1 pr:[property:reference URL] ?url1. FILTER(CONTAINS(STR(?url1), "www.europeanfilmacademy.org"))
#getting country of origin
?item p:[property:country of origin] ?st2.
#making sure the country of origin is sourced with a page from the domain "www.europeanfilmawards.eu"
?st2 ps:[property:country of origin] ?country; prov:wasDerivedFrom ?ref2.
?ref2 pr:[property:reference URL] ?url2. FILTER(CONTAINS(STR(?url2), "www.europeanfilmawards.eu"))
#getting the titles
?item wdt:[property:title] ?orig_title; rdfs:label ?label. FILTER(LANG(?label)="en")
BIND(IF(LANG(?orig_title) IN ("en", "en-gb", "en-us") || STR(?orig_title)=STR(?label), ?orig_title, CONCAT(?orig_title, " (", ?label, ")")) AS ?title)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}
ORDER BY ?year ?countryLabel

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
?topic1 ?topic1Label ?topic2 ?topic2Label
WITH {
SELECT
(COUNT(?work) AS ?count) ?topic1 ?topic2
WHERE {
# Find works that are marked with main subject of the topic.
?work wdt:[property:main subject] / ( wdt:[property:instance of]*/wdt:[property:subclass of]* | wdt:[property:part of]+ | wdt:[property:facet of]+ ) wd:[entity:SARS-CoV-2] .
# Identify co-occuring topics.
?work wdt:[property:main subject] ?topic1, ?topic2 .
# Exclude the topic it self
FILTER (wd:[entity:SARS-CoV-2] != ?topic1 && wd:[entity:SARS-CoV-2] != ?topic2 && ?topic1 != ?topic2)
}
GROUP BY ?topic1 ?topic2
ORDER BY DESC(?count)
# There a performance problems in the browser: We cannot show large graphs,
# so we put a limit on the number of links displayed.
LIMIT 400
} AS %results
WHERE {
INCLUDE %results
# Label the results
SERVICE wikibase:label {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en,da,de,es,fr,jp,nl,no,ru,sv,zh".
}
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

select
?quantity
(sample(?label) as ?label)
(sample(?desc) as ?desc)
(sample(?symbol) as ?symbol)
?formula
(
strdt(
concat(
"<math><mtable columnalign=left>",
group_concat(?symbolAndLabel),
"</mtable></math>"
),
<http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML>
) as ?otherSymbols
)
where {
?quantity wdt:[property:subclass of]+ wd:[entity:individual quantity] .
optional { ?quantity rdfs:label ?label . filter (lang(?label) = "en") }
optional { ?quantity schema:description ?desc . filter (lang(?desc) = "en") }
?quantity wdt:[property:defining formula] ?formula .
?quantity wdt:[property:in defining formula] ?symbol .
{
select distinct * where {
?quantity p:[property:calculated from] [ pq:[property:in defining formula] ?otherSymbol ; ps:[property:calculated from] / rdfs:label ?otherLabel ] .
filter (lang(?otherLabel) = "en")
bind (
concat(
"<mrow>",
str(?otherSymbol), "<mtext>", ": ", ?otherLabel, "</mtext>",
"</mrow>"
) as ?symbolAndLabel
)
}
}
}
group by ?quantity ?formula
limit 500

MINUS { ?comm2 p:[property:instance of] [ ps:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:metro station] ] } .
?comm2 wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord2 .
?comm1 p:[property:coordinate location] [ ps:[property:coordinate location] []; psv:[property:coordinate location] [ wikibase:geoLongitude ?coord1lon; wikibase:geoLatitude ?coord1lat; ] ] .

SELECT ?q1 ?q2 ?label ?coord1 ?coord2 ?dist ?layer ?line WHERE {
?q1 wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:commune of France] ; rdfs:label ?label ; wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord1 . FILTER (lang(?label) = "fr").

?q2 wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:commune of France] ; rdfs:label ?label ; wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord2 . FILTER (lang(?label) = "fr").
?q2 p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location] ?valuenode2. ?valuenode2 wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2 . ?valuenode2 wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2.
FILTER ( str(?q1) > str(?q2) )
BIND(geof:distance(?coord1, ?coord2) AS ?dist).
BIND(floor(?dist/100) AS ?layer).
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING (', STR(?lon1), ' ', STR(?lat1), ',', STR(?lon2), ' ', STR(?lat2), ')') AS ?str) .
BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
FILTER ( ?dist > 100 )
}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?person ?personLabel (MAX(?end_or_now) as ?last_date) (MAX(?age_end_or_now) as ?age_at_date) (?when - YEAR(?last_date) as ?years_alive_since) ?dob ?dod ?when ?age
{
VALUES ?office { wd:[entity:Vice President of the United States] wd:[entity:President of the United States] }
?st ps:[property:position held] ?office .
?person wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human]; p:[property:position held] ?st .
OPTIONAL { ?st pq:[property:end time] ?e }
BIND( COALESCE(?e, NOW() ) as ?end_or_now)
?person wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dob .
OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:[property:date of death] ?dod } .
BIND( COALESCE( YEAR( ?dod) , YEAR(NOW()) ) as ?when )
BIND( ?when - YEAR(?dob) as ?age)
BIND(YEAR(?end_or_now)-YEAR(?dob) as ?age_end_or_now)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en" }
}
GROUP BY ?person ?personLabel ?dob ?dod ?age ?when
ORDER BY DESC(?age)
