PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?station ?stationLabel ?coords ?line ?layer ?rgb (SAMPLE(?image) AS ?image) (sample(?opening) as ?opening) WHERE {
?station wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:metro station];
wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]* wd:[entity:Stockholm County];
wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coords;
p:[property:adjacent station] ?pred.
?pred ps:[property:adjacent station] ?conn;
pq:[property:connecting line] ?subwayLine.
MINUS { ?pred pq:[property:end time] [] }
OPTIONAL { ?station wdt:[property:image] ?image }.
OPTIONAL { ?station wdt:[property:date of official opening] ?opening }.
?conn wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?cds;
wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:metro station].
BIND(IF(xsd:double(?depth/10) = xsd:integer(?depth/10),?cds,"") as ?coords)
?conn p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1 .
?station p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2 .
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING(', STR(?lon1), ' ', STR(?lat1), ',', STR(?lon2), ' ', STR(?lat2), ')') AS ?str) . BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
?subwayLine wdt:[property:sRGB color hex triplet] ?rgb .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "sv". ?subwayLine rdfs:label ?layer. ?station rdfs:label ?stationLabel }
}
GROUP BY ?station ?stationLabel ?coords ?line ?layer ?rgb

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?author ?authorLabel ?birthplaceLabel ?idGND ?coord ?country
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?occupation_label; SEPARATOR=", ") as ?occupations) #thanks to @NavinoEvans for this!
WHERE {
?author wdt:[property:GND ID] ?idGND . #has a GND id
?author wdt:[property:sex or gender] wd:[entity:female] . #is female
?author wdt:[property:occupation] wd:[entity:writer] . #is writer
?author wdt:[property:place of birth] ?birthplace . # born in a place...
?birthplace wdt:[property:country] ?country . # which is in a country that is...
?country p:[property:part of]/ps:[property:part of] wd:[entity:Latin America] . # part of Latin America thanks Tony Bowden! (@tmtm)
?birthplace wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord .
OPTIONAL {
?author wdt:[property:occupation] ?occupation . #get occupation
?occupation rdfs:label ?occupation_label FILTER (lang(?occupation_label) = "en") #get label the 'manual' way
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} GROUP BY ?author ?authorLabel ?birthplaceLabel ?idGND ?coord ?country #GROUP BY
LIMIT 5000

PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX ontolex: <http://www.w3.org/ns/lemon/ontolex#>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT (uri(replace(str(?l), "L", "Q")) as ?item) (MD5(CONCAT(str(?item),str(RAND()))) as ?random) ?l ?hitza ?sense ?ahotsak ?elhuyar ?audio (SAMPLE(?picture_) AS ?picture) WHERE
{
?l a ontolex:LexicalEntry ; dct:language ?language ; wikibase:lemma ?hitza ; ontolex:sense ?esanahia.
?esanahia skos:definition ?sense; wdt:[property:item for this sense] ?q_concept.
?q_concept wdt:[property:image] ?picture_.
?language wdt:[property:ISO 639-1 code] 'eu'.
FILTER (LANG(?sense) = 'eu')
OPTIONAL {?l wdt:[property:Ahotsak lexeme] ?ahotsak.}
OPTIONAL {?l wdt:[property:Elhuyar Dictionary ID] ?elhuyar.}
?l ontolex:lexicalForm ?f .
?f ontolex:representation ?form ; wdt:[property:pronunciation audio] ?audio .
filter (regex(str(?f), "-F1$")) .
# Exclude out of scope concepts
MINUS {?q_concept wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:sovereign state].}. # countries
MINUS {?l wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:nonce].}. #ad hoc hitzak
# Exclude non suitable concepts
VALUES ?minus {
wd:[entity:rape] # rape
wd:[entity:war] # war
wd:[entity:violence] # violence
wd:[entity:revolver] # revolver
wd:[entity:cigar] #cigar
#... add yours here
}.
MINUS {?sense wdt:[property:item for this sense] ?minus.}.
# Exclude senses not suitable for young children:
MINUS {
VALUES ?filter { wd:[entity:slang] wd:[entity:pejorative] wd:[entity:vulgarism] wd:[entity:insult] wd:[entity:profanity] }
?esanahia wdt:[property:language style] ?filter.
}
}
GROUP BY ?l ?sense ?hitza ?ahotsak ?elhuyar ?audio
ORDER BY ?random
LIMIT 1

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?start ?parl_start ?age ?dob ?dod WHERE {
VALUES ?parl {wd:[entity:Member of Parliament] wd:[entity:Member of Parliament of Great Britain] wd:[entity:Member of Parliament in the Parliament of England]}
?item p:[property:position held] ?pos_stmt .
?pos_stmt ps:[property:position held] ?pos .
?pos wdt:[property:subclass of] ?parl .
OPTIONAL {
?pos_stmt pq:[property:start time] ?start .
}
OPTIONAL {
?pos wdt:[property:inception] ?parl_start .
}
BIND(COALESCE(?start, ?parl_start) AS ?best_start) .
?item p:[property:date of birth] ?dob_stmt .
?dob_stmt ps:[property:date of birth] ?dob .
FILTER(isLiteral(?dob)) .
?dob_stmt psv:[property:date of birth]/wikibase:timePrecision ?dob_precision .
FILTER(?dob_precision > 8) .
BIND (((?best_start - ?dob)/365.24) AS ?age) .
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:date of death] ?dod} .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} ORDER BY DESC(?age)
LIMIT 200

SELECT DISTINCT ?countryLabel ?hgovernmentLabel ?gage ?hstateLabel ?sage WHERE {
?country wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:sovereign state].
FILTER(NOT EXISTS { ?country wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:historical country]. })
?country p:[property:head of government] ?statement.
?statement ps:[property:head of government] ?hgovernment.

FILTER(NOT EXISTS { ?statement pq:[property:end time] ?x. })
?country p:[property:head of state] ?sstatement.

BIND((YEAR(NOW())) - (YEAR(?dobh)) AS ?gage)
?hstate wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dobs.

SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personLabel ?office ?officeLabel ?end1 ?start2 (FLOOR(?days/36.525)/10 AS ?gap)
WHERE {
# Offices Held by Heads of Government
?country wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:sovereign state]; p:[property:office held by head of government]/ps:[property:office held by head of government] ?office .
# People who have held the office more than once
?person p:[property:position held] [ ps:[property:position held] ?office ; pq:[property:end time] ?end1 ] .
?person p:[property:position held] [ ps:[property:position held] ?office ; pq:[property:start time] ?start2 ] .
FILTER (?start2 > ?end1)
FILTER NOT EXISTS { # but must be successive periods
?person p:[property:position held] [ ps:[property:position held] ?office ; pq:[property:start time] ?start3 ] .
FILTER((?start3 > ?end1) && (?start3 < ?start2))
}
# How long between end of one term and start of the next
BIND (?start2 - ?end1 AS ?days)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY DESC(?days)
LIMIT 10

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?winnerLabel1 ?ballsize ?rgb WHERE {
# the snooker ball colours
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?wins = 1, "ff0000", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 2, "ffff00", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 3, "00ff00", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 4, "8b4513", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 5, "0000ff", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 6, "ffc0cb", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 7, "000000", 1/0),
IF(?wins = 8, "ffa500", 1/0),
"800080"
) AS ?rgb )
BIND(1 AS ?ballsize)
BIND( CONCAT(?winnerLabel, ": ", STR(?wins)) AS ?winnerLabel1)
# inner select generates the winners totals
{ SELECT ?winnerLabel (COUNT (?winner) AS ?wins) WHERE {
{ ?p wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:World Snooker Championship] }
UNION
{ ?p wdt:[property:part of] wd:[entity:World Snooker Championship] }
?p wdt:[property:winner] ?winner .

}

IF(((?month=4)&&(?day>=20))||((?month=5)&&(?day<21)),"Taurus",
IF(((?month=5)&&(?day>=21))||((?month=6)&&(?day<21)),"Gemini",
IF(((?month=6)&&(?day>=21))||((?month=7)&&(?day<23)),"Cancer",
IF(((?month=7)&&(?day>=23))||((?month=8)&&(?day<23)),"Leo",
IF(((?month=8)&&(?day>=23))||((?month=9)&&(?day<23)),"Virgo",
IF(((?month=9)&&(?day>=23))||((?month=10)&&(?day<23)),"Libra",
IF(((?month=10)&&(?day>=23))||((?month=11)&&(?day<22)),"Scorpio",
IF(((?month=11)&&(?day>=23))||((?month=12)&&(?day<22)),"Sagittarius",

IF(((?month=1)&&(?day>=20))||((?month=2)&&(?day<19)),"Aquarius",
IF(((?month=2)&&(?day>=19))||((?month=3)&&(?day<21)),"Pisces",
"unknown (this should never happen)"
))))))))))))
AS ?sign)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language 'en' }
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

select (str(?decade) as ?dec) (count(distinct ?ps) as ?count) ?causeLabel where
{
?mp p:[property:position held] ?ps . ?ps ps:[property:position held] ?term . ?term wdt:[property:subclass of] wd:[entity:Member of Parliament] .
?ps pq:[property:end time] ?pend . filter not exists { ?mp p:[property:position held] ?ps2 . ?ps2 ps:[property:position held] ?term . ?ps2 pq:[property:start time] ?pend }
# not new term starting same day - ie left Parliament
?ps pq:[property:end cause] ?cause .
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:dissolution of parliament] } # not dissolution
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:Suspension from the UK parliament] } # not suspension
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:suspension from a political party] } # tofix
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:election as Speaker of the House] } # tofix
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:leaving party] } # tofix
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:joining party] } # tofix
filter not exists { ?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:rejoining party] } # tofix
bind(year(?pend) as ?year) . filter(?year >= 1880) . bind((floor(?year/10)*10) as ?decade) .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} group by ?causeLabel ?decade order by ?causeLabel
#defaultView:BarChart

select distinct ?person ?personLabel ?old_seatLabel ?resigned ?new_seatLabel ?elected ?diff where
{
?term wdt:[property:subclass of] wd:[entity:Member of Parliament] .
?person p:[property:position held] ?ps1 . ?ps1 ps:[property:position held] ?term . ?ps1 pq:[property:start time] ?s1 . ?ps1 pq:[property:end time] ?resigned .
?ps1 pq:[property:electoral district] ?old_seat . ?ps1 pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:resignation] .
?person p:[property:position held] ?ps2 . ?ps2 ps:[property:position held] ?term . ?ps2 pq:[property:start time] ?elected . ?ps2 pq:[property:electoral district] ?new_seat .
filter (?old_seat != ?new_seat) .
filter (?elected > ?resigned) .
bind(round(?elected - ?resigned) as ?diff) .
filter not exists {
?person p:[property:position held] ?ps3 . ?ps3 ps:[property:position held] ?term . ?ps3 pq:[property:start time] ?s3 . ?ps3 pq:[property:end time] ?e3 .
filter (?s3 > ?resigned ) . filter (?elected > ?e3 ) }
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} order by desc(?elected)

?item p:[property:coordinates of westernmost point]/psv:[property:coordinates of westernmost point]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?west .
?item wdt:[property:inception] ?year .

INCLUDE %colours .
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:image] ?img} .
?item wdt:[property:described at URL] ?url .
?item wdt:[property:external georeferencing URL] ?georeferencing .
BIND(STRDT( CONCAT('LINESTRING (',
str(?west), ' ', str(?sth), ',',
str(?west), ' ', str(?nth), ',',
str(?east), ' ', str(?nth), ',',
str(?east), ' ', str(?sth), ',',
str(?west), ' ', str(?sth), ')' ), geo:wktLiteral) AS ?bbox) .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
?article
(SUM(?male) AS ?count_males)
(SUM(?female) AS ?count_females)
(SUM(?nonbinary) AS ?count_nonbinary)
(COUNT(*) AS ?count)
(ROUND(100 * ?count_females / (?count_females + ?count_males + ?count_nonbinary)) AS ?share_females)
(ROUND(100 * ?count_nonbinary / (?count_females + ?count_males + ?count_nonbinary)) AS ?share_nonbinary)
(ROUND(100 * ?count_males / (?count_females + ?count_males + ?count_nonbinary)) AS ?share_males)
{
VALUES ?article {
"Anthropology"
"Philosophy"
"Economics"
"Sociology"
"Demography"
}
SERVICE wikibase:mwapi {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:endpoint "en.wikipedia.org";
wikibase:api "Generator";
mwapi:generator "links";
mwapi:titles ?article;.
?item wikibase:apiOutputItem mwapi:item.
}
FILTER BOUND (?item)
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] .
?item wdt:[property:sex or gender] ?gender .
BIND(IF(?gender IN(wd:[entity:male], wd:[entity:trans man]), 1, 0) AS ?male )
BIND(IF(?gender IN(wd:[entity:female], wd:[entity:trans woman]), 1, 0 ) AS ?female)
BIND(IF(?gender = wd:[entity:non-binary], 1, 0) AS ?nonbinary)
}
GROUP BY ?article

query:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?x ?xLabel ?description ?x_coords ?rgb WITH {
SELECT ?data ?x ?x_coords WHERE {
?x p:[property:elevation above sea level]/psn:[property:elevation above sea level] [
wikibase:quantityAmount ?data
] .
?x wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?x_coords .
?x wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:Sweden] .
# ?x wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]+ [ wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:principal area of Wales] ] .
}
} AS %data
# determine the max and min values (used to calculate the spread)
WITH {
SELECT (MAX(?data) AS ?max_data) (MIN(?data) AS ?min_data) WHERE {
INCLUDE %data
}} AS %min_max
WHERE {
INCLUDE %data
INCLUDE %min_max
?x rdfs:label ?xLabel. FILTER (LANG(?xLabel) = "sv") .
BIND (CONCAT("Hojd over havsnivan for ", ?xLabel, " ar omkring ", STR(ROUND(?data)), " meter" ) AS ?description)
BIND ( ?max_data - ?min_data AS ?spread )
BIND (255 - xsd:integer( 255 * (?data - ?min_data) / ?spread) AS ?green ) # 255 -> 0
BIND ( FLOOR (?green / 16) AS ?green_1 )
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?green_1 < 10, STR(?green_1), 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?green_1 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?green_hex1 )
BIND (FLOOR(?green - (16 * xsd:integer( ?green / 16 ))) AS ?green_2)
BIND ( COALESCE(
IF(?green_2 < 10, STR(?green_2), 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 10, "a", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 11, "b", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 12, "c", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 13, "d", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 14, "e", 1/0),
IF(?green_2 = 15, "f", 1/0),
"ERROR"
) AS ?green_hex2 )
BIND (CONCAT(STR(?green_hex1), STR(?green_hex2)) AS ?green_hex )
BIND (CONCAT("00", STR(?green_hex), "00") AS ?rgb)
}

minus{?ps pq:[property:elected in] ?elec.?elec wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:United Kingdom general election].?mp p:[property:position held][ps:[property:position held] ?t0; pq:[property:parliamentary group] ?p; pq:[property:electoral district] ?s; pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:dissolution of parliament]].?t0 wdt:[property:followed by] ?t}

{SELECT distinct ?mp ?mpLabel ?pLabel ?sLabel ?end

minus{?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:dissolution of parliament].?mp p:[property:position held][ps:[property:position held] ?t2;pq:[property:parliamentary group] ?p;pq:[property:electoral district] ?s;pq:[property:elected in] ?elec].?t2 wdt:[property:follows] ?t.?elec wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:United Kingdom general election]}
minus{?ps pq:[property:end cause] wd:[entity:returned for another seat and chose to sit there]}#omit untaken double-return seats
SERVICE wikibase:label{bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en"}}ORDER BY ?mp ?end}
filter(?end > ?start)#> not >=
}group by ?mp ?mpLabel ?pLabel ?sLabel ?start order by ?start

FILTER(?station != wd:[entity:Dibrugarh railway station])
?pred p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1 .

BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING(', STR(?lon1), ' ', STR(?lat1), ',', STR(?lon2), ' ', STR(?lat2), ')') AS ?str) . BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)

}

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

?human wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] .
?human wdt:[property:country of citizenship] wd:[entity:United Kingdom] .
?human wdt:[property:sex or gender] ?gender .
?human p:[property:date of death] [
a wikibase:BestRank ;
psv:[property:date of death] [
wikibase:timeValue ?dateOfDeath ;
wikibase:timePrecision ?precision
]
]
FILTER (?precision >= 10 ) # month precision or better
BIND(YEAR(?dateOfDeath) as ?year) .
BIND(MONTH(?dateOfDeath) as ?month) .
BIND ( IF(?month < 10, CONCAT("0",STR(?month) ), STR(?month)) AS ?MM)
BIND(CONCAT(STR(?year), "-", ?MM) as ?deathYYYY_MM).
FILTER (?year >= 2005)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
GROUP BY ?deathYYYY_MM ?genderLabel

query:
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT * WHERE {
wd:[entity:The Antartic Circumpolar Voyage] p:[property:location] ?stat .
?stat ps:[property:location] ?location .
?location p:[property:coordinate location] [ ps:[property:coordinate location] []; psv:[property:coordinate location] [ wikibase:geoLongitude ?coord1lon; wikibase:geoLatitude ?coord1lat; ] ].
?stat pq:[property:series ordinal] ?series .
wd:[entity:The Antartic Circumpolar Voyage] p:[property:location] ?stat2 .
?stat2 ps:[property:location] ?location2 .
?location2 p:[property:coordinate location] [ ps:[property:coordinate location] []; psv:[property:coordinate location] [ wikibase:geoLongitude ?coord2lon; wikibase:geoLatitude ?coord2lat; ] ].
?stat2 pq:[property:series ordinal] ?series2 .
filter (xsd:integer(?series) = xsd:integer(?series2) -1)
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING (', STR(?coord1lon), ' ', STR(?coord1lat), ',', STR(?coord2lon), ' ', STR(?coord2lat), ')') AS ?str) .
BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
BIND("ff0033" as ?rgb)
BIND("voyage" AS ?layer)
}

query:
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?line WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:Czech Republic] .
?item wdt:[property:coordinate location] [] .
?item p:[property:coordinate location] ?statement1, ?statement2 filter(?statement1 != ?statement2).
{?statement1 pq:[property:start time] [] .} union {?statement1 pq:[property:end time] [] .}
{?statement1 pq:[property:start time] [] .} union {?statement2 pq:[property:end time] [] .}
?statement1 ps:[property:coordinate location] []; psv:[property:coordinate location] [ wikibase:geoLongitude ?coord1lon; wikibase:geoLatitude ?coord1lat; ].
?statement2 ps:[property:coordinate location] []; psv:[property:coordinate location] [ wikibase:geoLongitude ?coord2lon; wikibase:geoLatitude ?coord2lat; ].
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING (', STR(?coord1lon), ' ', STR(?coord1lat), ',', STR(?coord2lon), ' ', STR(?coord2lat), ')') AS ?str) .
BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
?nv ?item ?itemLabel
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?l0; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?all)
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?l1; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?all_ad)
?enl
WHERE
{
{
SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?nv ?enl (STR(?lt) AS ?l0) (STR(?ln) AS ?l1)
WHERE
{
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:ordinal number]; wdt:[property:numeric value] ?nv . FILTER( ?nv < 101 )
?item rdfs:label ?enl. FILTER( LANG(?enl) = "en" )
?item (rdfs:label|skos:altLabel) ?lt . FILTER( STR(?lt) != STR(?enl) && !CONTAINS(?lt, str(?nv) ) )
?item (rdfs:label|skos:altLabel) ?ln . FILTER( STR(?ln) != STR(?enl) && CONTAINS(?ln, str(?nv) ) )
}
ORDER BY ?nv ?l0
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE]". }
}
GROUP BY ?nv ?item ?itemLabel ?enl
ORDER BY ?nv

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?lexeme ?offset ?representation ?qLabel ?example {
?lexeme p:[property:usage example] ?example_statement .
?example_statement ps:[property:usage example] ?example .
?example_statement pq:[property:subject form] ?form .
?form ontolex:representation ?representation .
?lexeme wikibase:lemma ?lemma .
BIND(STRLEN(STRBEFORE(?example, ?representation)) AS ?offset)
?lexeme dct:language wd:[entity:Danish] .
OPTIONAL {
?example_statement pq:[property:subject sense] / wdt:[property:item for this sense] ?q
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}

?item wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity] ?else .

where

SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en".

?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel .}
}

?geo

SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pLabel ?pImage ?m ?mLabel ?mImage
WITH{SELECT DISTINCT ?m ?m_s ?m_e WHERE{
INCLUDE %start_US . VALUES $MONARCH{wd:[entity:monarch] wd:[entity:king] wd:[entity:queen]} VALUES $GB_UK {wd:[entity:United Kingdom] wd:[entity:United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland] wd:[entity:Kingdom of Great Britain]}
?m wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human];p:[property:position held] ?ph.?ph pq:[property:start time] ?m_s{?ph ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:monarch of the United Kingdom]}UNION{?ph ps:[property:position held] $MONARCH; pq:[property:of] $GB_UK}
OPTIONAL{?ph pq:[property:end time] ?m_e}FILTER(?m_s >= ?start_US || ?m_e >= ?start_US)
BIND(NOW() AS ?today)BIND(COALESCE(?m_e, ?today) as ?m_e)}}AS %monarchs
WITH{SELECT ?start_US WHERE{?x wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human];p:[property:position held] ?ph.?ph ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:President of the United States];pq:[property:series ordinal] ?number;pq:[property:start time] ?start_US.
FILTER(?number = "1")}}AS %start_US
WHERE{INCLUDE %monarchs.
?p wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human];p:[property:position held] ?node.?node ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:President of the United States];pq:[property:start time] ?p_s;pq:[property:series ordinal] ?number.OPTIONAL{?node pq:[property:end time] ?p_e}
BIND(NOW() AS ?today)BIND(COALESCE(?p_e, ?today) as ?p_e)FILTER( (?m_s >= ?p_s && ?m_s <= ?p_e)||(?m_e >= ?p_s && ?m_e <= ?p_e )||(?p_s >= ?m_s && ?p_s <= ?m_e)||(?p_e >= ?m_s && ?p_e <= ?m_e))
OPTIONAL{?m wdt:[property:image] ?mImage}BIND(COALESCE(?mImage, <http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/IIH.png>) as ?mImage)
OPTIONAL{?p wdt:[property:image] ?pImage}BIND(COALESCE(?pImage, <http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/IIH.png>) as ?pImage)
SERVICE wikibase:label{bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en".}
}

?case wdt:[property:judge] ?justice;
wdt:[property:cites work] ?report.

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?date ?winner ?winnerLabel ?pm ?pmLabel ?pm_image WITH {
SELECT DISTINCT ?winner ?d WHERE { # all the winners of the English Premier League or First Division
VALUES $ENGLISH_FIRST { wd:[entity:Football League First Division] wd:[entity:Premier League] wd:[entity:English Football League] }
?x wdt:[property:sports season of league or competition] $ENGLISH_FIRST .
?x wdt:[property:winner] ?winner .
?x wdt:[property:end time] ?d
MINUS { ?x wdt:[property:league level above] [] } # make sure this is really the Top league
}} AS %winners
WITH {
SELECT (MAX(?d) AS ?date) ?winner WHERE { # get the latest (MAX) date
INCLUDE %winners
} GROUP BY ?winner} AS %winner_and_date
WHERE { # determine who was the Prime minister on a particular date
INCLUDE %winner_and_date
?pm p:[property:position held] ?ph_stmt .
OPTIONAL { ?pm wdt:[property:image] ?pm_image }
?ph_stmt ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:Prime Minister of the United Kingdom] .
?ph_stmt pq:[property:start time] ?pm_start .
OPTIONAL { ?ph_stmt pq:[property:end time] ?pm_end }
BIND(COALESCE(?pm_end, NOW()) AS ?pm_end)
FILTER (?pm_start <= ?date && ?pm_end >= ?date)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?date

SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
?award wdt:[property:subclass of] wd:[entity:Nobel Prize].

SELECT ?decade (SUM(?female) AS ?count_females) (SUM(?male) AS ?count_males) (COUNT(*) AS ?count) ((100 * ?count_females) / ?count AS ?share_female) WHERE {
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
?award wdt:[property:subclass of] wd:[entity:Nobel Prize].
?item p:[property:award received] _:b1;
wdt:[property:sex or gender] ?gender.
_:b1 ps:[property:award received] ?award;
pq:[property:point in time] ?date.

}
GROUP BY ?decade

gas:program gas:linkType wdt:[property:adjacent station] . } }
FILTER(?station != wd:[entity:Narvik])
?pred p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1 .
?station p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2 .
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING(', STR(?lon1), ' ', STR(?lat1), ',', STR(?lon2), ' ', STR(?lat2), ')') AS ?str) . BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)

}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?weekday (count(distinct(?item)) as ?count) WHERE {
wd:[entity:World War II] wdt:[property:start time] ?od ; wdt:[property:end time] ?do.
?item wdt:[property:place of death] wd:[entity:Mauthausen concentration camp] .
?item p:[property:date of death] [ps:[property:date of death] ?date ; psv:[property:date of death]/wikibase:timePrecision ?precision ] filter(?precision = 11 && day(?date) != 1 && ?date > ?od && ?date < ?do ).
BIND( DAY( ?date ) AS ?q ) .
BIND( MONTH( ?date ) + IF( MONTH( ?date ) < 3, 12, 0 ) AS ?m ) .
BIND( YEAR( ?date ) - IF( MONTH( ?date ) < 3, 1, 0 ) AS ?_year ) .
BIND( ?_year - FLOOR( ?_year / 100 ) * 100 AS ?K ) . # modulo
BIND( FLOOR( YEAR( ?date ) / 100 ) AS ?J ) .
BIND( ?q + FLOOR( 13 * ( ?m + 1 ) / 5 ) + ?K + FLOOR( ?K / 4 ) + FLOOR( ?J / 4 ) - 2 * ?J AS ?_h ) .
BIND(( ?_h - FLOOR( ?_h / 7 ) * 7) as ?day) .
BIND(if(?day=0,"06 (Saturday)",if(?day=1,"07 (Sunday)",if(?day=2,"01 (Monday)",if(?day=3,"02 (Tuesday)",if(?day=4,"03 (Wednesday)",if(?day=5,"04 (Thursday)",if(?day=6,"05 (Friday)",""))))))) as ?weekday) .
} group by ?weekday order by asc(?weekday)

PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
?word
(COUNT(*) as ?count)
(URI(CONCAT("https://www.wikidata.org/w/index.php?search=inlabel%3A",?word,"%40[AUTO_LANGUAGE]+-haswbstatement%3A%2A&profile=advanced&fulltext=1&ns=1")) as ?search)
WITH
{
SELECT ?item (CONCAT(?n, " 1 1 1 1 1 1 1 1 ") as ?string)
{
?item wikibase:statements 0 .
[] schema:about ?item ; schema:name ?n ; schema:isPartOf <https://[AUTO_LANGUAGE].wikipedia.org/>
}
LIMIT 20000
} as %aa
WITH
{
SELECT (str(?nv-1) as ?ord) { [] wdt:[property:KIT Linked Open Numbers ID] ?i ; wdt:[property:numeric value] ?nv . FILTER( ?nv < 8) }
} as %i
WHERE
{
INCLUDE %i
INCLUDE %aa
BIND( CONCAT("^([^ ]+ ){",?ord,"}([^ ]+) .+$") as ?re)
BIND( REPLACE(?string, ?re, "$2") as ?word)
# FILTER( ?word != "1" && )
FILTER( strlen(?word) > 4)
}
GROUP BY ?word
ORDER BY DESC(?count)
LIMIT 100

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
PREFIX gas: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf/gas#>

SELECT ?station ?line (CEIL(?depth/10)*10 as ?layer) ?coord {
SERVICE gas:service {
gas:program gas:gasClass "com.bigdata.rdf.graph.analytics.BFS" ; gas:in wd:[entity:Rīga Pasažieru] ; gas:out ?station ; gas:out1 ?depth ; gas:out2 ?pred .
gas:program gas:linkType wdt:[property:adjacent station] . }
FILTER(?station != wd:[entity:Rīga Pasažieru])
?pred wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?cds.
BIND(IF(xsd:double(?depth/10) = xsd:integer(?depth/10),?cds,"") as ?coords)
?pred p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1 .
?station p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2 ; p:[property:coordinate location]/psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2 .
values ?country { wd:[entity:Latvia] wd:[entity:Lithuania] wd:[entity:Estonia] wd:[entity:Russia] wd:[entity:Belarus] } ?station wdt:[property:country] ?country .
# only Baltics or Russia or Belarus
BIND(CONCAT('LINESTRING(', STR(?lon1), ' ', STR(?lat1), ',', STR(?lon2), ' ', STR(?lat2), ')') AS ?str) . BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "bn,en". }
?station wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord.
}

SELECT ?station ?stationLabel ?subwayLine ?coords ?line ?line_number ?layer ?rgb WHERE {
VALUES ?search { wd:[entity:Coast Tram] #light rail system search
}
?search wdt:[property:has part(s)]|wdt:[property:item operated] ?lignes.#what are the lines of that light rail?
?lignes wdt:[property:terminus] ?termini.#what are the termini of the lines of that light rail
?station wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:public transport stop]; #any type of service station
wdt:[property:state of use] wd:[entity:in use];#That are running
wdt:[property:transport network] ?search;#That are part of the searched light rail network
wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coords;
wdt:[property:connecting line]|wdt:[property:connecting service] ?subwayLine;
wdt:[property:adjacent station] ?pred.
?pred wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coords_pred;wdt:[property:state of use] wd:[entity:in use];#Neighbours that are running
wdt:[property:connecting line]|wdt:[property:connecting service] ?subwayLine_pred.
?station p:[property:adjacent station] _:b1.
_:b1 ps:[property:adjacent station] ?pred ;
pq:[property:towards] ?towards;
pq:[property:connecting line]|pq:[property:connecting service] ?line_pq.
?subwayLine wdt:[property:state of use] wd:[entity:in use].#Lines that are running
optional{?subwayLine wdt:[property:route number] ?line_number.}
FILTER(?subwayLine_pred = ?lignes)#take only the lines if correspondance on the same line
FILTER(?subwayLine = ?lignes)
FILTER(?subwayLine = ?line_pq)#Take only the lines if next station on the same line
FILTER(?towards = ?termini)
?pred p:[property:coordinate location] ?node_pred .
?node_pred psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1 ;psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1 .
?node_pred a wikibase:BestRank.
?station p:[property:coordinate location] ?node_station.
?node_station psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2 ;psv:[property:coordinate location]/wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2.
?node_station a wikibase:BestRank.
BIND(CONCAT("LINESTRING(", STR(?lon1), " ", STR(?lat1), ",", STR(?lon2), " ", STR(?lat2), ")") AS ?str)
BIND(STRDT(?str, geo:wktLiteral) AS ?line)
?subwayLine wdt:[property:sRGB color hex triplet] ?rgb.
SERVICE wikibase:label {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en" .
?subwayLine rdfs:label ?layer.
?pred rdfs:label ?predLabel.
?station rdfs:label ?stationLabel .
} } GROUP BY ?station ?stationLabel ?subwayLine ?rgb ?predLabel ?layer ?coords ?line ?line_number
ORDER BY xsd:integer(?line_number) ?line_number ?subwayLine

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>

PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?pm ?pmLabel ?pmImage ?monarch ?monarchLabel ?monarchImage WITH {
# not sure if there is a more straightforward way to access British monarchs (this query runs second)
SELECT DISTINCT ?monarch ?monarch_start ?monarch_end WHERE {
INCLUDE %start_UK .
VALUES $MONARCH { wd:[entity:Monarch of Great Britain] wd:[entity:monarch of the United Kingdom] wd:[entity:monarch of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland] }
?monarch wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] .
?monarch p:[property:position held] ?ph .
?ph ps:[property:position held] $MONARCH .
?ph pq:[property:start time] ?monarch_start .
OPTIONAL { ?ph pq:[property:end time] ?monarch_end }
FILTER (?monarch_start >= ?start_UK || ?monarch_end >= ?start_UK)
BIND ( NOW() AS ?today )
BIND(COALESCE(?monarch_end, ?today) as ?monarch_end) # handle missing end dates, hopefully it's just the current monarch
} } AS %monarchs
# Find the start date of the first Prime Minister so we can filter monarchs that reigned after this point (this query runs first)
WITH { SELECT ?start_UK WHERE {
?pm p:[property:position held] ?pmph_stmt .
?pmph_stmt ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:Prime Minister of the United Kingdom] .
?pmph_stmt pq:[property:start time] ?start_UK .
}
ORDER BY ?start_UK
LIMIT 1 } AS %start_UK
# this query runs last and uses the select in line 2; it produces the visualisation specified in line 1
WHERE {
INCLUDE %monarchs
?pm wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human] .
?pm p:[property:position held] ?node .
?node ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:Prime Minister of the United Kingdom] .
OPTIONAL { ?node pq:[property:start time] ?pm_start }
OPTIONAL { ?node pq:[property:end time] ?pm_end }
BIND ( NOW() AS ?today )
BIND(COALESCE(?pm_end, ?today) as ?pm_end) # handle missing end dates, hopefully it's just the current president
FILTER( (?monarch_start >= ?pm_start && ?monarch_start <= ?pm_end) || (?monarch_end >= ?pm_start && ?monarch_end <= ?pm_end ) ||
(?pm_start >= ?monarch_start && ?pm_start <= ?monarch_end) || (?pm_end >= ?monarch_start && ?pm_end <= ?monarch_end ))
# get images, use a default image if none found
OPTIONAL { ?monarch wdt:[property:image] ?monarchImage }
BIND(COALESCE(?monarchImage, <http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Image_needed,_please_upload_to_commons.wikimedia.org.jpg>) as ?monarchImage)
OPTIONAL { ?pm wdt:[property:image] ?pmImage }
BIND(COALESCE(?pmImage, <http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Image_needed,_please_upload_to_commons.wikimedia.org.jpg>) as ?pmImaage)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?controversies ?controversiesLabel ?sitelinks WHERE {
# find all "controversies" items using CirrusSearch (SPARQL isn't the right tool for this job)
SERVICE wikibase:mwapi {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:endpoint "www.wikidata.org";
wikibase:api "Search";
# note: the "inlabel" keyword also searches aliases
# exclude scholarly articles (Q13442814), there's plenty of them and we don't care about them here
# also exclude categories (Q4167836, [property:category contains]); we'll filter them out again below, but excluding some here speeds things up
mwapi:srsearch "inlabel:controversies@en -haswbstatement:[property:instance of]=Q13442814 -haswbstatement:[property:instance of]=Q4167836 -haswbstatement:[property:category contains]";
# get as many search results at once as possible
mwapi:srlimit "max".
?controversies wikibase:apiOutputItem mwapi:title.
}
# get the number of sitelinks and the English label
?controversies wikibase:sitelinks ?sitelinks;
rdfs:label ?controversiesLabel.
FILTER(LANG(?controversiesLabel) = "en")
# filter out categories (-haswbstatement:[property:instance of]=Q4167836 doesn't exclude categories that are instance of a subclass of Q4167836)
FILTER(!STRSTARTS(?controversiesLabel, "Category:"@en))
# also filter out templates (only one match at the moment, not worth adding this to the search string)
FILTER(!STRSTARTS(?controversiesLabel, "Template:"@en))
# filter out the item about the "controversy" concept
FILTER(?controversies != wd:[entity:controversy])
# require at least one sitelink (article)
FILTER(?sitelinks > 0)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?sitelinks)

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?st ?stLabel ?sl ?coords ?line ?layer ?rgb WHERE {
?search wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:tram system];wdt:[property:has part(s)] ?lignes.
?lignes wdt:[property:terminus] ?termini.
?st wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:tram stop];wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:France];(wdt:[property:part of]|wdt:[property:transport network]) ?search;wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coords;(wdt:[property:connecting line]|wdt:[property:connecting service]) ?sl;wdt:[property:adjacent station] ?pred;p:[property:adjacent station][ps:[property:adjacent station] ?pred;pq:[property:towards] ?towards;(pq:[property:connecting line]|pq:[property:connecting service]) ?line_pq].
?pred wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coords_pred;(wdt:[property:connecting line]|wdt:[property:connecting service]) ?sl_pred.
OPTIONAL{?sl wdt:[property:transport network]71 ?ln.}
FILTER(?sl_pred = ?lignes)FILTER(?sl = ?lignes)FILTER(?towards = ?termini)
MINUS{?st (wdt:[property:dissolved, abolished or demolished date]|wdt:[property:end time]|wdt:[property:date of official closure]) ?dispar.}
MINUS{?st (wdt:[property:state of use]|wdt:[property:state of conservation]) ?interdit.VALUES ?interdit{wd:[entity:proposed building or structure] wd:[entity:abandoned] wd:[entity:building or structure under construction] wd:[entity:on hold] wd:[entity:temporarily closed] wd:[entity:cancelled] wd:[entity:closed to the public] wd:[entity:decommissioned] wd:[entity:permanently closed]}}
?pred p:[property:coordinate location][psv:[property:coordinate location][wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat1;wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon1]; rdf:type wikibase:BestRank].
?st p:[property:coordinate location][psv:[property:coordinate location][wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat2;wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon2]; rdf:type wikibase:BestRank].
BIND(STRDT(CONCAT("LINESTRING(",STR(?lon1)," ",STR(?lat1),",",STR(?lon2)," ",STR(?lat2),")"),geo:wktLiteral)AS ?line)
?sl wdt:[property:sRGB color hex triplet] ?rgb.
SERVICE wikibase:label{bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "fr". ?sl rdfs:label ?layer. ?st rdfs:label ?stLabel}
}
GROUP BY ?st ?stLabel ?sl ?rgb ?layer ?coords ?line
ORDER BY ?ln ?sl

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?position_statement) AS ?ministerCount)
WHERE
{
# Essere umano di cittadinanza italiana
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human].
?item wdt:[property:country of citizenship] wd:[entity:Italy].
# Non piu vecchio/a di Mattarella

filter (?birth > "1941-07-23"^^xsd:dateTime).

pq:[property:start time] ?start FILTER (?start >= "2018-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime) . }
# Ex ministri
?item p:[property:position held] ?position_statement .
?position_statement ps:[property:position held]/wdt:[property:part of] wd:[entity:Council of Ministers of Italy].
# Ma non ministri recenti
MINUS { ?item p:[property:position held] ?position_recent .
?position_recent ps:[property:position held]/wdt:[property:part of] wd:[entity:Council of Ministers of Italy].
?position_recent pq:[property:end time] ?position_end
FILTER (?position_end >= "2014-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime). }
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],it". }
}
GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?bandLabel; SEPARATOR=", ") AS ?bands)

?band p:[property:instance of] ?statement1.

?band p:[property:genre] ?statement0.

?band wdt:[property:location of formation] ?city. # band formed in city
?city wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity]* ?state. # county in admin body (state)
?state wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:U.S. state]. # state is instance of US State
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en".
?state rdfs:label ?stateLabel.
?band rdfs:label ?bandLabel.}
}
GROUP BY ?state ?stateLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?bandCount)

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?layer ?article ?person ?personLabel ?personDescription ?coord ?pic ?picGrave ?DoD
WHERE {
?person wdt:[property:place of burial] wd:[entity:Père Lachaise Cemetery]; #Place of burial
p:[property:place of burial] [
pq:[property:burial plot reference] ?graveplot;
pq:[property:coordinate location] ?coord];
wdt:[property:date of death] ?DoD.
OPTIONAL{ ?person wdt:[property:image] ?pic .} # If we have an illustration
OPTIONAL{ ?person wdt:[property:image of grave] ?picGrave .} # If we have a picture of the grave
OPTIONAL {
?article schema:about ?person .
?article schema:inLanguage "fr" .
?article schema:isPartOf <https://fr.wikipedia.org/> .
}
OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:[property:sex or gender] ?group .} # Occupation in Layer
#BIND(year(?DoD) AS ?Deces)
BIND(
IF(?DoD < "1850-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime, "1800-1849",
IF(?DoD < "1900-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime, "1850-1899",
IF(?DoD < "1950-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime, "1900-1949",
IF(?DoD < "2020-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime, "1950-2000",
"2000-2022"))))
AS ?layer).
#FILTER (YEAR(?DoD) >= 2000)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "fr, en" .}
}

How many lexeme pairs exist between different languages?
List the language combinations with the most lexeme pairs.
What is the count of lexeme pairs for each language pair?
Show me the top 100 language pairs with the highest number of lexemes.

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX ontolex: <http://www.w3.org/ns/lemon/ontolex#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT
?language1 ?language1Label ?language2 ?language2Label
?number_of_lexemes
WITH {
SELECT ?language1 ?language2 (COUNT(*) AS ?number_of_lexemes) {
[] ^wdt:[property:item for this sense] / ^ontolex:sense ?lexeme1, ?lexeme2 .
FILTER (?lexeme1 != ?lexeme2)
?lexeme1 dct:language ?language1 .
?lexeme2 dct:language ?language2 .
FILTER (?language1 != ?language2)
FILTER (STR(?language1) > STR(?language2))
}
GROUP BY ?language1 ?language2
ORDER BY DESC(?number_of_lexemes)
LIMIT 100
} AS %result
{
INCLUDE %result
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY DESC(?number_of_lexemes)

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?xLabel ?size ?rgb WITH {
SELECT DISTINCT ?n WHERE { # generate a sequence of natural numbers
VALUES ?start { 1 }
BIND (2000 AS ?end)
BIND ( (?end - ?start ) + 1 AS ?x )
[] p:[property:instance of] [
ps:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:natural number] ; # is a natural number
pq:[property:follows] ?prev
] .
?prev wdt:[property:numeric value] ?n .
FILTER (?n > 0 && ?n < ?x + 1)
}
} AS %numbers
WHERE {
INCLUDE %numbers
?x wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:natural number] .
?x wdt:[property:numeric value] ?n .
FILTER (?x NOT IN (wd:[entity:0.999...])) # exclude the annoying 0.999
OPTIONAL { ?x wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:prime number] . BIND (true AS ?prime) } # highlight prime numbers
BIND(1 AS ?size) # used for the size of the bubble: want them all the same size
BIND ( COALESCE(IF(?prime, "FD7F7F", 1/0),"71C1FD") AS ?rgb )
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?n

PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT (?item AS ?QNumber) ?[property:ISO 639-3 code] ?LanguageLabel ?[property:number of speakers, writers, or signers] ?Qualifier_[property:point in time]
WHERE
{
VALUES ?instance_of { wd:[entity:language] wd:[entity:dialect] } # Language or dialect
?item wdt:[property:instance of] ?instance_of .
OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:[property:ISO 639-3 code] ?[property:ISO 639-3 code] . } # ISO 639 3 code
?item p:[property:number of speakers, writers, or signers] ?no_of_speakers_statement .
?no_of_speakers_statement wikibase:rank wikibase:PreferredRank . # Has preferred rank
?no_of_speakers_statement pq:[property:applies to part] wd:[entity:first language] . # Has the qualifier applies to part = first language
?no_of_speakers_statement ps:[property:number of speakers, writers, or signers] ?[property:number of speakers, writers, or signers] . # No of speakers
OPTIONAL { ?no_of_speakers_statement pq:[property:point in time] ?Qualifier_[property:point in time] . } # Optional timestamp
SERVICE wikibase:label
{
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en" .
?item rdfs:label ?LanguageLabel .
}
}
ORDER BY DESC(?[property:number of speakers, writers, or signers])

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription (COUNT(*) AS ?count) WHERE {
VALUES ?target {
wd:[entity:Elizabeth]
wd:[entity:Elisabeth]
wd:[entity:Élisabeth]
}
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human];
p:[property:given name] ?statement.
?statement ps:[property:given name] ?target.
OPTIONAL { ?statement pq:[property:series ordinal] ?rank. }
BIND(IF(BOUND(?rank),?rank, 0) AS ?rank2)
FILTER(xsd:integer(?rank2) < xsd:integer(2))
?sitelink schema:about ?item.
FILTER (SUBSTR(str(?sitelink), 11, 15) = ".wikipedia.org/") .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "fr,en". }
}
GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription
ORDER BY DESC (?count)
LIMIT 100

query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?title ?wd_coord ?wiki_coord ?dist
WITH
{
SELECT DISTINCT ?item
{
?item wdt:[property:instance of] / wdt:[property:subclass of] * wd:[entity:railway station] .
?item wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:United Kingdom] .
FILTER STRENDS(STR(?item), "0")
}
} AS %get_items
{
INCLUDE %get_items
?item p:[property:coordinate location] ?s .
?s ps:[property:coordinate location] ?wd_coord .
?s prov:wasDerivedFrom ?ref .
?ref pr:[property:imported from Wikimedia project] wd:[entity:English Wikipedia] .
?sitelink schema:about ?item .
?sitelink schema:isPartOf <https://en.wikipedia.org/> .
?sitelink schema:name ?title .
SERVICE wikibase:mwapi
{
bd:serviceParam wikibase:endpoint "en.wikipedia.org" .
bd:serviceParam wikibase:api "Generator" .
bd:serviceParam mwapi:generator "allpages" .
bd:serviceParam mwapi:gapfrom ?title .
bd:serviceParam mwapi:gapto ?title .
bd:serviceParam mwapi:prop "coordinates" .
?lat wikibase:apiOutput "coordinates/co/@lat" .
?lon wikibase:apiOutput "coordinates/co/@lon" .
}
BIND (STRDT(CONCAT("Point(", ?lon, " ", ?lat, ")"), geo:wktLiteral) AS ?wiki_coord)
BIND (geof:distance(?wd_coord, ?wiki_coord) AS ?dist)
FILTER (! BOUND(?dist) || ?dist > 0.0)
} ORDER BY DESC(?dist)

wdt:[property:publication date] ?datetimes.
[] wdt:[property:cites work] ?work;
wdt:[property:author] ?winner.
?winner wdt:[property:award received] ?nobel.
BIND(xsd:date(?datetimes) AS ?dates)
SERVICE wikibase:label {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en".
?winner rdfs:label ?winnerLabel.
?work rdfs:label ?workLabel.
}
}

WHERE
{
wd:[entity:FIFA World Cup 2022 Sticker Album] p:[property:image]0 [

] .

pq:[property:start time] ?national_team_debut
] .

FILTER(LANG(?national_team_label) = "en")
FILTER (!CONTAINS ( ?national_team_label,"under"))
FILTER (!CONTAINS ( ?national_team_label,"Olympic"))
OPTIONAL{?player wdt:[property:image] ?image .}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". } # Helps get the label in your language, if not, then en language
